Ecomm_Short_Description: Robust and full-bodied musky aroma with earthy terpenes.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Qwests Escape Qwest (Death Bubba) is cultivated using the mineral rich soils and streams of the Pacific Northwest. A heavy indica, Death Bubba presents a robust flower structure, which yields earthy terpenes of wood and pine. With bright pistils and bulbous trichomes, Death Bubba has a familiar musk reminiscent of other BC-grown favourites.

CBD God Bud possesses an overwhelmingly fresh aroma of lemon-lime, pine and eucalyptus. Hand-trimmed in the Okanagan to preserve the quality and maximum trichome retention.

Ecomm_Long_Description: Small flowers from high-quality sativa products are put through a specialized milling process. Ecomm_Long_Description: With distinct orange hairs snaking off crystal-heavy flowers, 8 Ball Kush features a rich earthy smell with skunky accents. A product of breeding Bubba Kush with King Kush, this potent strain has an almost hash-like flavour that is punctuated with spicy notes. Cured to maintain natural moisture and maximum terpene retention.

Cured to maintain natural moisture and maximum terpene retention.

Ecomm_Long_Description: High-THC indica-dominant cannabis, known for its generous crystals against its dark green and purple colouring, creating the appearance of a star. It has an earthy, pungent aroma and flavour.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Strong musky and floral scent, with a sweet flavour.
Ecomm_Long_Description: This earthy, honey flavored strain originated from modern day Pakistan and Afghanistan. It has all of the qualities of a medium-high THC indica-dominant strain, with just a sprinkle of sativa to keep it blended.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Strong musky and floral scent, with a sweet flavour.
Ecomm_Long_Description: This earthy, honey flavored strain originated from modern day Pakistan and Afghanistan. It has all of the qualities of a medium-high THC indica-dominant strain, with just a sprinkle of sativa to keep it blended.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Fresh blueberry and vanilla notes make this strain taste as good as it smells.
Ecomm_Long_Description: A potent indica that has been grown by breeder DJ Short as part of his exotic landrace collection. These hand-trimmed, grape-shaped buds feature vibrant blue undertones and frosty, thick trichome crystals that taste like they smell: pungent blueberry with hints of vanilla accented by fragrant florals. A cross between Afghani, Thai, and Purple Thai strains.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Aromatic berry dessert flavour with hints of caramel and coffee.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Finding roots in Northern California's Mendocino County, The Purps also holds a strong Canadian connection after BC Bud Depot developed a stable cross to make seeds available to Canuck growers. This popular variety is known for its upfront fragrance and taste. It expresses an earthy, nutty flavour of blended berries accented by hints of caramel and coffee.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Hand-trimmed, trichome-frosted flowers with a sweet lemon and citrus flavour.
Ecomm_Long_Description: A cross of Lemon OG Kush and a Nigerian Hashplant, this landrace hybrid offers a strong flavour coupled by large, airy buds with vibrant yellow-orange pistils and a danky aroma of lemon mixed with hints of coffee, earth and sour spice. The strong citrus influence indicates high levels of the terpene limonene (found in citrus fruits). Hand-trimmed.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Fresh blueberry and vanilla notes make this strain taste as good as it smells.
Ecomm_Long_Description: A potent indica that has been grown by breeder DJ Short as part of his exotic landrace collection. These hand-trimmed, grape-shaped buds feature vibrant blue undertones and frosty, thick trichome crystals that taste like they smell: pungent blueberry with hints of vanilla accented by fragrant florals. A cross between Afghani, Thai, and Purple Thai strains.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Aromatic berry dessert flavour with hints of caramel and coffee.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Finding roots in Northern California's Mendocino County, The Purps also holds a strong Canadian connection after BC Bud Depot developed a stable cross to make seeds available to Canuck growers. This popular variety is known for its upfront fragrance and taste. It expresses an earthy, nutty flavour of blended berries accented by hints of caramel and coffee.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Hand-trimmed, trichome-frosted flowers with a sweet lemon and citrus flavour.
Ecomm_Long_Description: A cross of Lemon OG Kush and a Nigerian Hashplant, this landrace hybrid offers a strong flavour coupled by large, airy buds with vibrant yellow-orange pistils and a danky aroma of lemon mixed with hints of coffee, earth and sour spice. The strong citrus influence indicates high levels of the terpene limonene (found in citrus fruits). Hand-trimmed.

Ecomm_Long_Description: Known as a potent sativa-dominant hybrid strain with moderate-to-high THC content. White Shark offers a leading myrcene terpene profile. A deep earthy and musky flavour with a hint of fruit, this strain is a cross between Super Skunk, Brazilian and South Indian strains.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Bright and fresh citrus flavour with an earthy, floral aroma.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Developed by The Netherlands Green House Seeds in the 1990s, White Widow plants are chunky, conical, and tapered; the structures of the flowers are more like sativa than indica, with a loose and fluffy texture that can be broken up somewhat easily, despite its stickiness. It holds a fairly balanced 60/40 sativa/indica ratio and its limonene terpene gives White Widow a citrusy and peppery scent, accompanied by a slight lemony aftertaste. A cross between Brazilian and South Indian strains.

Ecomm_Long_Description: BC Bud Depot originally created God Bud by mixing an almost pure sativa called Hawaiian with a purple indica strain called Purple Skunk. The resin-coated bud features  herbal, musky flavours combined with tropical fruit and undertones of berry, lavender, and pine. The aromas can be described as tropical, earthy, and citrusy.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Fruity indica-dominant hybrid with a berry-forward aroma.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Shishkaberry is an indica-dominant hybrid and its lineage is attributed to a cross between DJ Short Blueberry with an Afghani strain called The Red. The buds are dense spade-shaped dark olive green with minty green leaves and undertones that are specked with furry dark amber hairs and frosty with thick white trichomes. Shishkaberry tastes of fresh-picked, earthy berries that sweetens upon exhale with a fruity/berry aroma to match. It has a moderately high THC level.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC hybrid with a cherry aroma.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Redecan Black Cherry Punch is a high-THC, indica-dominant hybrid, known for its bold cherry, yet light skunky flavour profile. The signature aroma comes from a diverse collection of terpenes that create aromas such as fruit, wood, spice, and pine, thanks to genetics from the classic strains Black Cherry Pie and Purple Punch. It has a terpene profile of limonene, myrcene, and beta-caryophyllene.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sativa-dominant hybrid with a sweet and sour taste.

Cheesequakes flowers are small to medium in size and hold together in the dense, popcorn-like bud structure typical of indicas. This strain comes through on the nose with a sour, tangy funk combined with clashing floral, berry, and grape notes underneath. This pungent aroma and slight tea flavour are commonly associated with cheese hybrids.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Musky aroma coupled with a herbal taste profile.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Cold Creek Kush is a hybrid that crosses the powerful MK Ultra with fellow Colorado native Chemdawg 91. The plant has a recognizable dank smell, much like a forest after a rainfall. Its taste profile is strongly herbal and almost overpowering. On the exhale its flavours turn earthy and woody, with a pleasant shock of fresh and sour pine. Cold Creek Kush grows into a tall plant with dense branches covered in thick buds and trichomes.

Ecomm_Long_Description: The Balmoral strain is a THC-dominant hybrid that is a variety of UK Cheese with Skunk #1 lineage. Its forest green buds are complemented by orange pistils. Caryophyllene and humulene are the terpenes that give this strains aroma spicy hints of hops and cloves.

Ecomm_Long_Description: This high-THC, sativa strain is a variety of Chemdawg, one of the original parent strains of several diesel cultivars, including East Coast Sour Diesel, OG Kush, and Headband. Caryophyllene and pinene add subtle hints of cloves and pine to this strain's aroma.

Ecomm_Long_Description: This indica-dominant THC strain has Afghan ancestry and dense, trichome-rich flowers. The terpene profile tends to lead with myrcene and balances out with notes of clove and pine from caryophyllene and pinene.

Ecomm_Long_Description: Houndstooth is a sativa-dominant, high-THC strain, bred by crossing Grandaddy Purple with Platinum Cookies. Its buds have a purple hue and possess a complex aroma from the terpenes myrcene, which tends to have a sweet and earthy scent, as well as caryophyllene, which is also found in cloves. It also has notes of pine from pinene and citrus from limonene.

Ecomm_Long_Description: Marley Gold Jack Herer was named after the late cannabis activist. Sourced from B.C. genetics and greenhouse grown in Ontario its a bright and potent strain. It's parent strains include Haze, Shiva Skunk, and Northern Lights #5.

Terpenes like terpinolene, caryophyllene and myrcene lend to its flavour, evoking flowers, earth and fruit. Ecomm_Long_Description: Canadian-grown dried cannabis with delicate aromas of citrus and pine, reminiscent of the lush forests of Western Canada, where the strain originated. Made with 100 percent Time Warp cannabis, laboratory tested for potency and purity.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Canadian-grown pre-roll with earthy, herbaceous, and lightly sweet aromas.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Canadian-grown dried cannabis defined by earthy and herbaceous aromas, complemented by a hint of sweetness. Made with 100 percent Hash Plant cannabis, laboratory tested for potency and purity.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Canadian-grown pre-roll with refreshing aromas of citrus and pine.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Canadian-grown dried cannabis that is true to its name, with vibrant colours and lingering aromas and flavours of sweet vanilla and fresh berries. Made with 100 percent Island Pink cannabis, laboratory tested for potency.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Strong musky and floral scent, with a sweet flavour.
Ecomm_Long_Description: This earthy, honey flavored strain originated from modern day Pakistan and Afghanistan. It has all of the qualities of a medium-high THC indica-dominant strain, with just a sprinkle of sativa to keep it blended.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Super-potent, sativa-dominant strain with deep notes of pine and lemony diesel.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Ultra Sour is a super-potent, sativa-dominant strain with spade-shaped flowers that are dark green and fragrant with fiery orange tendrils. Ultra Sour is trichome-rich and features deep notes of pine and lemony diesel. Parent strains include MK Ultra and East Coast Sour Diesel.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC, sativa-dominant strain with deep notes of pine and lemony diesel.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Ultra Sour is a high-THC, sativa-dominant strain with spade-shaped flowers that are dark green and fragrant with fiery orange tendrils. Ultra Sour is trichome-rich and features deep notes of pine and lemony diesel. Parent strains include MK Ultra and East Coast Sour Diesel.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Low-THC strain with fluffy green flowers and bright orange hairs.
Ecomm_Long_Description: A low-THC strain, Namaste CBD is a phenotype of Cannatonic. Namaste CBD sports fluffy, vivid green flowers, with bright orange hairs.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Low-THC, high-CBD strain with fluffy green flowers and bright orange hairs.
Ecomm_Long_Description: A low-THC and high-CBD strain, Namaste CBD is a phenotype of Cannatonic. Namaste CBD sports fluffy, vivid green flowers, with bright orange hairs.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sweet, fruity fragrance with notes of red berries and blueberries.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Shishkaberry has a sweet, fruity fragrance with notes of red berries and blueberries. The flower itself is dense and covered with a mass of thick, sticky trichomes. The flowers are a mosaic of green and purple, with a mass of dark amber hairs. This strain contains moderately high THC levels and can exhibit both sativa and indica characteristics. Shiskhaberry is a cross between DJ Short Blueberry and an unknown Afghani strain.

Ecomm_Long_Description: Ultra Sour is a sativa-dominant strain with spade-shaped flowers that are dark green and fragrant with fiery orange tendrils. Ultra Sour is trichome-rich and features deep notes of pine and lemony diesel. Ultra Sour is a cross between MK Ultra and East Coast Sour Diesel.

Ultra Sour is trichome-rich and features deep notes of pine and lemony diesel. Ultra Sour is a cross between MK Ultra and East Coast Sour Diesel.

The flowers are a mosaic of green and purple, with a mass of dark amber hairs. This indica-dominant strain contains moderately high THC levels and can exhibit both sativa and indica characteristics. Shishkaberry is a cross between DJ Short Blueberry and an unknown Afghani strain.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Subtle aroma of exotic fruits and citrus, rounded off by an earthy flavour.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Carefully grown indoors, this hand-trimmed blend has a balance of THC and CBD.  Durga Mata 2 is a steadfast strain that produces robust flower clusters at the end of its growing period. It has a subtle aroma that is reminiscent of exotic fruits and citrus, rounded off by a grounding earthy flavour.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Earthy and sweet flavours from highly resinous, dense flowers.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Derived from the resinous flower of Durga Mata, this strain produces robust flower clusters at the end of its growing period. Subtle aromas of exotic fruits and citrus, rounded off with an earthy flavour in a THC:CBD blend.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Balanced 1:1 THC:CBD extract, diluted in MCT oil.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Balancing the effects of THC and CBD, Namaste 1:1 THC:CBD oil is an alternative for consumers who prefer ingestion over vaporization. The extracted cannabis concentrate of this oil is diluted in MCT oil, which makes it easily absorbed by the body. The effects of Namaste 1:1 oil are delayed compared to inhaled cannabis and can last significantly longer than vaporized cannabis. Consumers are cautioned to start low and go slow.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Floral and earthy flavour with hints of blueberries.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Sativa-dominant Blue Haze comes from the parentage of indica-dominant Blueberry and sativa-dominant Haze, giving it a floral and earthy flavour with hints of blueberries.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Aromas are a mixture of earthy and flowery tones.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Blue Haze is a sativa-dominant strain with mid-to-high THC content.  Its large, dense, and furry flower structure gives off the unmistakable smell of blueberries.  Subtle earthy and flowery undertones linger with the fruity notes of this strain without any  tart or skunky notes.  Due to its genetic similarity, Blue Haze has a similar profile to the Blue Dream strain.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sativa-dominant strain with citrus flavours and aromas.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Cali-O (aka California Orange) is a sativa-dominant strain that dates back to the 1980s. It features sweet citrus flavours and aromas.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Aromas of sweet orange and citrus zest.
Ecomm_Long_Description: With balanced THC and CBD, this variety of Cali-O is a 50:50 indica/sativa hybrid strain that dates back to the 1980s. Its tight leafy flower structure is coupled with a smell that is initially pungent and skunky though easily masked by the strong citrus base. Cali-O features sweet orange and citrus zest undertones.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Hybrid with sweet, tropical, mango flavours.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Mango Haze is a hybrid from the parents strains of Afghani and KC 33 with resulting sweet, tropical, mango flavours.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Aromas of citrus with sweet, tropical mango undertones.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Mango Haze is a sativa-dominant hybrid with a balanced THC to CBD ratio whose parents include Afghani and KC 33. The large, elongated crystalline flowers, often shaped like pine cones, are commonly intertwined with hairy yellow and orange pistils. Mango Haze carries a distinctive and uplifting citrus-heavy aroma with sweet, tropical mango undertones.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sativa-dominant strain with strawberry flavours and hints of mint.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Sativa-dominant strain with fresh strawberry flavours and a subtle minty undertone.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Aromas of delicate sweet berry undertones.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Strawberry Ice is a fruity sativa-dominant strain that is high in THC with very little CBD.  Its large and extremely dense flowers are thickly coated by trichomes and intertwined with dark orange hairs that often give the flower a slight red hue. Strawberry Ice is characterized by its distinct smell of fresh cut strawberries and refreshing mint undertones.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Notes of sour citrus and earthy pine, with woody undertones.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Rug Burn OG (Ghost OG) is a phenotype of the OG Kush strain. This indica-dominant strain features notes of sour citrus and earthy pine, with woody undertones.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC strain with pungent sour citrus aromas and hints of diesel.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Hand-harvested, high-THC, indica-dominant strain from the Ghost OG lineage with pungent sour citrus aromas and hints of diesel.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Indica-dominant strain with floral notes of linalool.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Scotts OG is an indica-dominant strain that comes from a lineage of Triangle Kush crossed with Rare Dankness #1. Floral linalool is the dominant terpene in the strain.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC strain with earthy, sweet, and sour notes.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Hand-harvested, high-THC, indica-dominant strain from a Triangle Kush and Rare Dankness #1 lineage. Earthy, sour, and sweet citrus aromas, with floral notes from the terpene linalool.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sativa-dominant strain with spicy, floral and citrus notes.
Ecomm_Long_Description: A sativa-dominant strain with notes of floral, citrus, and hints of spice. Ghost Train Haze comes from parent strains Ghost OG (indica-dominant) and Nevils Wreck (sativa-dominant).

Ecomm_Short_Description: Aromas of pine and citrus with a strong skunky presence.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Ghost Train Haze is a sativa-dominant hybrid with prominent THC levels. Ghost Train Haze emits a blend of pine and citrus aromas with a strong skunky presence.  It has bright green flowers that are dense, rich with trichomes and coated in light orange hairs. It is a cross between Ghost OG and Nevil's Wreck.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sativa-dominant phenotype of the high-CBD Cannatonic strain.
Ecomm_Long_Description: ACDC is a sativa-dominant phenotype of the high-CBD Cannatonic strain, know for its earthy, woody and piney aromas.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sativa-dominant phenotype of the high-CBD Cannatonic strain.
Ecomm_Long_Description: ACDC is a sativa-dominant phenotype of the high-CBD Cannatonic strain, know for its earthy, woody and piney aromas.

Ecomm_Short_Description: CBD-rich cannabis oil from the hybrid ACDC strain.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Ingestible high-CBD cannabis oil extracted from the hybrid ACDC strain, which is a sativa-dominant phenotype of the high-CBD Cannatonic strain, know for its earthy, woody and piney aromas. This oil has an MCT base and comes with a syringe-style dropper.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Ingestible sativa-dominant cannabis oil.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Ingestible sativa-dominant Blue Haze extract oil that comes from a flower that has the parentage of indica-dominant Blueberry and sativa-dominant Haze, giving it a floral and earthy flavour with hints of blueberries.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sativa-dominant cannabis oil.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Cali-O (aka California Orange) oil is extracted from a flower that  is a sativa-dominant strain that dates back to the 1980s. It features sweet citrus flavours and aromas.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Hybrid Mango Haze cannabis oil.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Mango Haze is a hybrid from the parents strains of Afghani and KC 33 with resulting sweet, tropical, mango flavours. Available in a cannabis oil format.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Ingestible sativa-dominant cannabis oil.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Ingestible cannabis extract oil from a sativa-dominant strain that has fresh strawberry flavours and a subtle minty undertone.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sativa-dominant phenotype of the high-CBD Cannatonic strain.
Ecomm_Long_Description: ACDC is a sativa-dominant phenotype of the high-CBD Cannatonic strain, know for its earthy, woody and piney aromas.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Floral and earthy flavour with hints of blueberries.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Sativa-dominant Blue Haze comes from the parentage of indica-dominant Blueberry and sativa-dominant Haze, giving it a floral and earthy flavour with hints of blueberries.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Aromas of sweet orange and citrus zest.
Ecomm_Long_Description: With balanced THC and CBD, this variety of California Orange is a 50:50 indica/sativa hybrid strain that dates back to the 1980s. Its tight leafy flower structure is coupled with a smell that is initially pungent and skunky though easily masked by the strong citrus base. Cali-O features sweet orange and citrus zest undertones.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Hybrid with sweet, tropical, mango flavours.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Mango Haze is a hybrid from the parents strains of Afghani and KC 33 with resulting sweet, tropical, mango flavours.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sativa-dominant strain with strawberry flavours and hints of mint.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Sativa-dominant strain with fresh strawberry flavours and a subtle minty undertone.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Earthy, skunky, and sweet flavours.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Blueish, sour-smelling flower, featuring a combination of earthy, skunky, and sweet flavours. Dark Star is a cross between Purple Kush and Mazar I Sharif.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Earthy, skunky, and sweet flavours.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Blueish, sour-smelling flower, featuring a combination of earthy, skunky, and sweet flavours. Dark Star is a cross between Purple Kush and Mazar I Sharif.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Earthy, skunky, and sweet flavours.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Blueish, sour-smelling flower, featuring a combination of earthy, skunky, and sweet flavours. Dark Star is a cross between Purple Kush and Mazar I Sharif.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Ingestible CBD-rich cannabis oil.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Potent, indica-dominant ingestible cannabis oil that comes from blueish, sour-selling flower that features a combination of earthy, skunky, and sweet flavours. Dark Star is a cross between Purple Kush and Mazar I Sharif.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC cannabis oil.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Blue Sky uses a proprietary extraction process. Terpenes have been removed.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC cannabis oil.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Extracted from a boutique strain and grown under specialized conditions, Low Gear is a high-THC cannabis oil that has had the terpenes removed.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-CBD cannabis oil.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Made using a specialized high-CBD strain under a proprietary growth and extraction method. Terpenes have been removed.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC, sativa-dominant cannabis oil.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Made from a sativa-dominant strain, Skylark is a high-THC cannabis oil that has had the terpenes removed.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sweet berry aromas with notes of tart apple and sour grape.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Also known as White Berry, this indica-dominant flower has medium dense, earthy green buds, a plethora of pistils and a thick, luscious coating of frosted trichomes. As its name implies, it has a sweet berry aroma balanced out by a bold sourness, and a multi-fruit flavour with plenty of bright blueberry rounded out with hints of tart apple and sour grape. It is a cross between White Widow and Blueberry.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sativa-dominant strain with notes of floral, citrus, and hints of spice.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Ghost Train Haze is a sativa-dominant strain with dense flowers that are a lighter green with orange/golden tones. The lineage of Ghost Train Haze is Ghost OG crossed with Neviles Wreck. Ghost OG is an indica-dominant strain and Neviles Wreck is a sativa-dominant strain. Ghost Train Haze has notes of floral, citrus, and hints of spice.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-CBD ingestible cannabis oil with MCT base.
Ecomm_Long_Description: This pure, concentrated cannabis oil contains primarily CBD, with only trace amounts of THC, and is formulated to be taken orally using the syringe included with the bottle. The active cannabinoids have been extracted from the cannabis flower though a supercritical CO2 process and blended with pharmaceutical-grade MCT carrier oil.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sweet and woody, high-THC, sativa-dominant strain.
Ecomm_Long_Description: High-THC, sativa-dominant strain (Nebula) that comes from the Buddha Haze lineage and has sweet and woody notes.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC cannabis oil with an MCT base.
Ecomm_Long_Description: This pure, concentrated cannabis oil contains primarily THC, with only trace amounts of CBD, and is formulated to be taken orally using the syringe included with the bottle. The active cannabinoids have been extracted from the cannabis flower though a supercritical CO2 process and blended with our pharmaceutical-grade MCT carrier oil.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Proprietary strain with hints of blueberries and sweet floral undertones.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Blueberry Seagal is a WeedMD indica-dominant proprietary strain that has crisp concentrated hints of blueberries with sweet floral undertones. The flowers are light green with light orange hues throughout.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sativa-dominant strain with notes of pine, lemon, and grape.
Ecomm_Long_Description: White Shark is a sativa-dominant strain that is a cross between Super Skunk, Brazilian, and South Indian. Super Skunk is an indica-dominant strain, while Brazilian and South Indian are sativa-dominant. White Shark shows characteristics from both a sativa and an indica. The flowers are dense, light green and have subtle golden hues. The aroma consists of notes of pine, lemon and complementary grape undertones.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sativa-dominant hybrid with high-THC content and a unique terpene profile.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Pedro's Sweet Sativa is a Canadian-bred cross of a Dominican sativa with White Russian and an unknown indica. The result is a sativa-dominant hybrid that produces large, airy flowers with high-THC content and a unique terpene profile of humulene, pinene, caryophyllene, and myrcene.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Hybrid pre-rolls with sweet and sour aromas.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Hybrid of a Skunk and Afghani cross with sweet and sour aromas from the combination of terpenes such as pinene, caryophyllene, limonene and myrcene.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sour, vintage cheese aroma with a floral, pine aftertaste.
Ecomm_Long_Description: This sativa-dominant hybrid is a cross between Skunk #1 and Afghani strains. It has a light green flower that produces a sour smelling, vintage cheese aroma and has a floral, pine aftertaste.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Cannabis oil with balance of 1:1 and MCT base.
Ecomm_Long_Description: This cannabis oil harnesses both THC and CBD. The active cannabinoids have been extracted from the cannabis flower though a supercritical CO2 process and blended with a pharmaceutical-grade MCT carrier oil.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sweet berry aromas with notes of tart apple and sour grape.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Also known as White Berry, this indica-dominant flower has medium dense, earthy green buds, a plethora of pistils and a thick, luscious coating of frosted trichomes. As its name implies, it has a sweet berry aroma balanced out by a bold sourness, and a multi-fruit flavour with plenty of bright blueberry rounded out with hints of tart apple and sour grape. It is a cross between White Widow and Blueberry.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sweet berry aromas with notes of tart apple and sour grape.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Also known as White Berry, this indica-dominant flower has medium dense, earthy green buds, a plethora of pistils and a thick, luscious coating of frosted trichomes. As its name implies, it has a sweet berry aroma balanced out by a bold sourness, and a multi-fruit flavour with plenty of bright blueberry rounded out with hints of tart apple and sour grape. It is a cross between White Widow and Blueberry.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Vintage cheese and herbal aroma with sweet pine notes.
Ecomm_Long_Description: An indica-dominant strain that features vivid green flowers with little clusters of peachy pistils and an herbal aroma with vintage cheese and sweet pine notes.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sour, vintage cheese aroma with a floral, pine aftertaste.
Ecomm_Long_Description: This sativa-dominant hybrid is a cross between Skunk #1 and Afghani strains. The light green flower produces a sour-smelling, extra old cheddar cheese aroma and a floral, pine aftertaste.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Pre-rolls with a sweet, honey-like aroma and flavour.
Ecomm_Long_Description: TGIF (Nebula) is a strain from sativa-dominant Buddha Haze parentage. Featuring a sweet, honey-like aroma and flavour.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Indica-dominant flower with rich earthy, citrus, and pine aromas.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Indica-dominant mid-to-high THC flower from a White Widow lineage. Known for its potential to produce a thick layer of trichomes, White Light typically presents rich earthy, citrus, and pine aromas.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-CBD flower with notes of sweet berries and a rich earthy aroma.
Ecomm_Long_Description: High-CBD flower from a Hurkle lineage, which is a cross between high-CBD Harlequin and Querkle. This indica-dominant flower has notes of sweet berries blended with a rich earthy aroma.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-CBD Sungrown flower with notes of apple, blood orange, and grapefruit.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Tantalus Labs' Harlequin high-CBD flower features rich forest green colours and dark brown pistil hairs. Sungrown in BC, it has a sour nose with notes of apple, blood orange, and grapefruit. Harlequin has historically low THC levels, and this Tantalus Labs varietal offers a similar cannabinoid profile, with rich colours and scents.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sweet earthy pine scent with notes of lemon and pepper.
Ecomm_Long_Description: No 501. Shooting Star is also known as Jack Herer, which is named after a famed cannabis activist, and has a sweet earthy pine scent with notes of lemon and pepper.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-CBD, BC Sungrown flower with bold earthy aromas and hints of vanilla.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Skunk Haze's frosted green top colas feature a flavour profile of earthy scents with hints of vanilla. Tantalus Labs' Sungrown variant has notably high CBD content, and a diverse and balanced cannabinoid profile. As the name suggests, bold aromas and flavours are abundant. Haze is a parent strain.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-CBD, BC Sungrown flower with sweet floral flavours and spicy undertones.
Ecomm_Long_Description: With exceptionally high-CBD content and close to zero THC, this Sungrown strain has been long-flowered into lime green, sticky flowers. Its floral aroma features a lemony sweetness with undertones of earthy cedar box and spice. Its lineage includes a CBD-rich Haze strain.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Earthy, woody flavours and melony citrus notes in BC Sungrown cannabis.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Serratus is a Tantalus Labs staple with a name chosen to reflect its unique plant appearance. Chunky blocks of flower clusters sit atop long colas, mimicking the jagged ridge-like features of Serratus mountain. Clean, velvety earth notes give woody backbone to the lighter melony citrus, complementing the body and nose. Afghani is a parent strain.

Ecomm_Short_Description: BC Sungrown flower with sweet blueberry and caramel aromas.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Blue Dream is a high-THC, sativa-dominant strain. Full spectrum sunlight fuels excellent trichome production that powders this dark green-grey flower structure. The sweet, blueberry syrup aroma is complemented with brown sugar and caramel. Blueberry is a parent strain.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-CBD Sungrown flower with notes of apple, blood orange, and grapefruit.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Tantalus Labs' Harlequin high-CBD flower features rich forest green colours and dark brown pistil hairs. Sungrown in BC, it has a sour nose with notes of apple, blood orange, and grapefruit. Harlequin has historically low THC levels, and this Tantalus Labs varietal offers a similar cannabinoid profile, with rich colours and scents.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-CBD, BC Sungrown flower with bold earthy aromas and hints of vanilla.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Skunk Haze's frosted green top colas feature a flavour profile of earthy scents with hints of vanilla. Tantalus Labs' Sungrown variant has notably high CBD content, and a diverse and balanced cannabinoid profile.  As the name suggests, bold aromas and flavours are abundant. Haze is a parent strain.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-CBD, BC Sungrown flower with sweet floral flavours and spicy undertones.
Ecomm_Long_Description: With exceptionally high-CBD content and close to zero THC, this Sungrown strain has been long-flowered into lime green, sticky flowers. Its floral aroma features a lemony sweetness with undertones of earthy cedar box and spice. A CBD-rich Haze is a parent strain.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Earthy, woody flavours and melony citrus notes in BC Sungrown cannabis.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Serratus is a Tantalus Labs staple with a name chosen to reflect its unique plant appearance. Chunky blocks of flower clusters sit atop long colas, mimicking the jagged ridge-like features of Serratus mountain. Clean, velvety earth notes give woody backbone to the lighter melony citrus, complementing the body and nose. Afghani is a parent strain.

Ecomm_Short_Description: BC Sungrown flower with sweet blueberry and caramel aromas.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Blue Dream is a high-THC, sativa-dominant strain. Full spectrum sunlight fuels excellent trichome production that powders this dark green-grey flower structure. The sweet, blueberry syrup aroma is complemented with brown sugar and caramel. Blueberry is a parent strain.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-CBD sublingual cannabis spray with MCT base.
Ecomm_Long_Description: High-CBD sublingual cannabis oil spray. Each odourless and flavour-neutral spritz under the tongue delivers 0.1ml of oil, or 2mg of active cannabinoids.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC oral cannabis spray with MCT base.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Odourless and flavour-neutral, this THC-dominant cannabis oil oral spray contains a THC to CBD ratio of 20:0. Created to be spritzed under your tongue, each spray delivers 0.1ml of oil, or 2mg of active cannabinoids.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Balanced 1:1 THC/CBD cannabis oil spray with MCT base.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Balanced 1:1 cannabis oil spray that releases 0.1ml of oil with each spritz.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Pungent, herbaceous, citrusy strain with balanced THC and CBD.
Ecomm_Long_Description: A hybrid created through a cross of Purple Erkle and Bubba Kush strains, Bubba Erkles myrcene-forward aroma is very pungent, with OG influences of pine and lemon topped with sweet berry flavour. This hard-to-find flower has dark fluffy popcorn-shaped buds with dark red hairs, purple undertones, and a heavy blanket of lavender crystal trichomes.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Densely compacted flowers with a fruity and herbal taste.
Ecomm_Long_Description: CBD Shark Shock is the result of a pairing between White Widow and Skunk #1. Compact and resinous buds possess an intense aroma of dank, fruity sweetness combined with an unmistakable skunk aroma. This product features the crisp flavour of green apples, sour citrus, and sweet apricot, with a subtle hint of eucalyptus to finish.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC strain (Sour Diesel hybrid) with notes of citrus and diesel.
Ecomm_Long_Description: High-THC, indica-dominant hybrid from Sour Diesel lineage. Flowers are blanketed in white trichomes and feature a strong citrus aroma with notes of diesel.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Musky aroma coupled with a herbal taste profile.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Cold Creek Kush is a hybrid that crosses the powerful MK Ultra with fellow Colorado native Chemdawg 91. The plant has a recognizable dank smell, much like a forest after a rainfall. Its taste profile is strongly herbal and almost overpowering. On the exhale its flavours turn earthy and woody, with a pleasant shock of fresh and sour pine. Cold Creek Kush grows into a tall plant with dense branches covered in thick buds and trichomes.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Hybrid strain with a tropical flavour of citrus and earth.
Ecomm_Long_Description: God Bud was created by mixing an almost pure sativa called Hawaiian with a purple indica strain called Purple Skunk. The resin-coated bud features  herbal, musky flavours combined with tropical fruit and undertones of berry, lavender, and pine. The aromas can be described as tropical, earthy, and citrusy.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Earthy with a pungent aroma of hops and pine.
Ecomm_Long_Description: An indica-dominant variety strain with a unique, pungent aroma with sweet notes. The plant has a short and stocky growth habit that results in an appealing, dense bud structure. Its aroma has a hint of sweetness combined with earthy and citrusy notes.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Fruity indica-dominant hybrid with a berry-forward aroma.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Shishkaberry is an indica-dominant hybrid and its lineage is attributed to a cross between DJ Short Blueberry with an Afghani strain called The Red. The buds are dense spade-shaped dark olive green with minty green leaves and undertones that are specked with furry dark amber hairs and frosty with thick white trichomes. Shishkaberry tastes of fresh-picked, earthy berries that sweetens upon exhale with a fruity/berry aroma to match. It has a moderately high THC level.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Indica-dominant with a peppery and citrus-forward taste profile.
Ecomm_Long_Description: A dense, tightly packed bud that is often associated with indicas, Wappa sets itself apart with large, solid flowers that taper from a broad base to a sharply pointed tip. This bud has a strong yet sweet aroma that verges on skunkiness, which also comes through in the caryophyllene-forward taste profile.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sativa-dominant hybrid with an herbal, citrusy terpene profile.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Known as a potent sativa-dominant hybrid strain with moderate-to-high THC content. White Shark offers a leading myrcene terpene profile. A deep earthy and musky flavour with a hint of fruit, this strain is a cross between Super Skunk, Brazilian and South Indian strains.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Bright and fresh citrus flavour with an earthy, floral aroma.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Developed by The Netherlands Green House Seeds in the 1990s, White Widow plants are chunky, conical, and tapered; the structures of the flowers are more like sativa than indica, with a loose and fluffy texture that can be broken up somewhat easily, despite its stickiness. It holds a fairly balanced 60/40 sativa/indica ratio and its limonene terpene gives White Widow a citrusy and peppery scent, accompanied by a slight lemony aftertaste. It is a cross between a Brazilian strain and a variety from South India.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC concentrated cannabis extract oil.
Ecomm_Long_Description: This oil is extracted from cannabis flower using a CO2 extraction process. It has an MCT oil base.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC, sativa-dominant strain with notes of citrus and pine.
Ecomm_Long_Description: The Crown Jewel is Redecan's in-house cross between Super Silver Haze and Wappa. This strain is a 20-25% THC sativa with a piney and citrus forward profile.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC, sativa-dominant strain with notes of citrus and pine.
Ecomm_Long_Description: The Crown Jewel is Redecan's in-house cross between Super Silver Haze and Wappa. This strain is a 21-25% THC sativa with a piney and citrus forward profile.

Ecomm_Long_Description: Shishkaberry, also known as Kish, is a high-THC, indica-dominant hybrid of DJ Short Blueberry and an Afghani strain. Purple-tinged flowers feature sweet berry aromas with hints of blueberry.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-CBD flower with notes of sweet berries blended with a rich earthy aroma.
Ecomm_Long_Description: High-CBD flower from a Hurkle lineage, which is a cross between high-CBD  Harlequin and Querkle. This indica-dominant flower has notes of sweet berries blended with a rich earthy aroma.

Ecomm_Long_Description: A high-THC, hand-harvested, indica-dominant strain featuring refreshing citrus notes balanced by an earthy nuttiness. Made with Canadian-grown Sensi Star cannabis, laboratory-tested for potency and purity.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Indica pre-roll crafted with milled flower.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Indica pre-roll crafted from milled flower from Mongolian lineage. Even-burning, these cone-shaped, 0.5 gram joints come packaged in child-resistant, single-unit packaging.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Earthy, woody and herbal flavours in a milled flower pre-roll.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Sativa pre-roll -crafted from milled flower from the Wabanaki lineage. Even-burning, these cone-shaped, 0.5 gram joints come packaged in child-resistant, single-unit packaging. Earthy, woody and herbal flavours come from the prominent terpenes pinene, caryophyllene, myrcene and terpinolene.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Milled flower pre-roll with sativa and indica properties.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Hybrid pre-roll with sativa and indica properties, crafted from milled flower that comes from a City Lights (Critical Kush) lineage. Even-burning, these cone-shaped, 0.5 gram joints come packaged in child-resistant, single-unit packaging.

Ecomm_Long_Description: Formulated from a blend of indica-dominant cannabis and infused in ingestible sunflower oil base. This sublingual cannabis oil is extracted using an ethanol-based process.

Ecomm_Long_Description: Formulated from a blend of sativa-dominant cannabis and infused in a sunflower oil base. This sublingual cannabis oil is extracted using an ethanol-based process.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Hybrid cannabis oil.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Combining traditional sativa properties and traditional indica properties, this product is formulated from a blend of hybrid cannabis infused in an ingestible sunflower oil base. Extracted using an ethanol-based process.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-CBD oral cannabis oil with sunflower oil base.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Formulated from high-CBD cannabis and infused in an ingestible sunflower carrier oil. This cannabis oil is extracted using an ethanol-based process.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Floral, tangy flavour from top cola flower.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Hand-manicured and craft-cured, this special reserve strain is harvested from the top colas of the cannabis plant, representing the highest quality parts of the plant. This high-THC, indica-dominant strain from a Hash Plant lineage produces flowers with an extremely tight, dense structure and a radiant milky emerald hue. Floral, tangy, and fresh flavours.

Ecomm_Long_Description: High-THC strain from Sour Diesel lineage with a pungent diesel aroma, and notes of pine and pepper.

Ecomm_Long_Description: Potent high-THC strain from Sour Diesel lineage with prominent pinene terpenes and pungent piney and diesel style aromas.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Pungent diesel aroma with notes of pine and pepper.
Ecomm_Long_Description: High-THC strain from Sour Diesel lineage with a pungent diesel aroma, and notes of pine and pepper.

Ecomm_Long_Description: THC oil intended for intimate, personal use. Fleur de Lune Intimate Spray comes in a convenient spray bottle and contains THC from a proprietary blend from a Northern Lights variant. Kosher certified product. Not compatible with latex. Spray has an ingestible MCT oil base, however, this product is not intended for sublingual use.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC, indica-dominant, dried flower with blueberry aromas.
Ecomm_Long_Description: An indica-dominant, high-THC dried flower that comes from a lineage of Blueberry crossed with Northern Lights, giving a blueberry aroma and flavour.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC, indica-dominant, dried flower with blueberry aromas.
Ecomm_Long_Description: An indica-dominant, high-THC dried flower that comes from a lineage of Blueberry crossed with Northern Lights, giving a blueberry aroma and flavour.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-CBD, indica-dominant strain with floral and cheesy notes.
Ecomm_Long_Description: A high-CBD, indica-dominant strain that comes from a CBD Shark and Blue Cheese lineage and features a complex floral aroma with hints of cheese.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-CBD, indica-dominant strain with floral and cheesy notes.
Ecomm_Long_Description: A high-CBD, indica-dominant strain that comes from a CBD Shark and Blue Cheese lineage and features a complex floral aroma with hints of cheese.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC strain with piney aromas and hints of sweetness.
Ecomm_Long_Description: These flowers are dark green, dense, and covered in highly resinous trichomes. This high-THC cannabis strain is a unique 50/50 hybrid created by TH Seeds from an OG Kush and Burma Indica lineage.  It features aromas of pine with hints of sweetness.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC strain with piney aromas and hints of sweetness.
Ecomm_Long_Description: These high-THC flowers are dark green, dense, and covered in highly resinous trichomes. This cannabis strain is a unique 50/50 hybrid created by TH Seeds from an OK Kush and Burma Indica lineage. Featuring piney and floral flavours from prominent terpenes such as pinene and nerolidol.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC, indica-dominant flower with sweet, earthy notes.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Originating from Barney's Coffee Shop in Amsterdam, Cookie Kush is a potent, high-THC, indica-dominant flower that comes from a lineage of GSC and OG Kush. Prominent terpenes such as pinene, limonene, caryophyllene, myrcene, and linalool give it an earthy, sweet, and pungent aroma.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC, indica-dominant flower with sweet, earthy notes.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Originating from Barney's Coffee Shop in Amsterdam, Cookie Kush is a potent, high-THC, indica-dominant flower that comes from a lineage of GSC and OG Kush. Prominent terpenes such as pinene, limonene, caryophyllene, myrcene, and linalool give it an earthy, sweet, and pungent aroma.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-CBD, sativa-dominant with notes of sweet, fruity oranges.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Sativa-dominant Dinamed is a high-CBD, low-THC, 60/40 sativa to indica hybrid that smells and tastes like sweet and fruity oranges. It is a cross between Pure CBD #4 and Pure CBD strains.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-CBD, sativa-dominant with notes of sweet, fruity oranges.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Sativa-dominant Dinamed is a high-CBD, low-THC, 60/40 sativa to indica hybrid that smells and tastes like sweet and fruity oranges. It is a cross between Pure CBD #4 and Pure CBD strains.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Spicy, pine-scented, high-THC, sativa strain.
Ecomm_Long_Description: A spicy, pine-scented, high-THC, sativa created in the Netherlands in the mid 1990s. Jack Herer is a cross between Northern Lights #5 and Shiva Skunk. Dominant terpenes include pinene, caryophyllene, limonene, and linalool.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Spicy, pine-scented, high-THC, sativa strain.
Ecomm_Long_Description: A spicy, pine-scented, high-THC, sativa created in the Netherlands in the mid 1990s. Jack Herer is a cross between Northern Lights #5 and Shiva Skunk. Dominant terpenes include pinene, caryophyllene, limonene, and linalool.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC, indica-dominant strain with citrus, pepper, floral, and pine notes.
Ecomm_Long_Description: High-THC, indica-dominant, flower with limonene, caryophyllene, linalool and pinene terpenes that give citrus, pepper, floral, and pine notes. Brightly coloured flowers have dense calyx, thickly coated with resin. Gabriola has a very robust smell and look, as an indica-dominant  hybrid with complicated genetic history unique to Broken Coast. Frost Monster is a parent strain.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC, indica-dominant strain with citrus, pepper, floral, and pine notes.
Ecomm_Long_Description: High-THC, indica-dominant, flower with limonene, caryophyllene, linalool and pinene terpenes that give citrus, pepper, floral, and pine notes. Brightly coloured flowers have dense calyx, thickly coated with resin. Frost Monster has a very robust smell and look, as an indica-dominant hybrid with complicated genetic history unique to Broken Coast.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC, indica-dominant strain with citrus, pepper, floral, and pine notes.
Ecomm_Long_Description: High-THC, indica-dominant, flower with limonene, caryophyllene, linalool and pinene terpenes that give citrus, pepper, floral, and pine notes. Brightly coloured flowers have dense calyx, thickly coated with resin. Gabriola has a very robust smell and look, as an indica-dominant hybrid with complicated genetic history unique to Broken Coast. Frost Monster is a parent strain.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Hints of blueberries with sweet floral undertones.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Blueberry Seagal is a WeedMD indica-dominant proprietary strain that has been hand-selected by phenotype hunters. This strain has crisp concentrated hints of blueberries while harbouring sweet floral undertones. The flowers are light green with light orange hues throughout.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sativa-dominant strain with notes of floral, citrus, and hints of spice.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Ghost Train Haze is a sativa-dominant strain with dense flowers that are a lighter green with orange/golden tones. The lineage of Ghost Train Haze is Ghost OG crossed with Neviles Wreck. Ghost OG is an indica-dominant strain and Neviles Wreck is a sativa-dominant strain. Ghost Train Haze has notes of floral, citrus, and hints of spice.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sativa-dominant strain with notes of pine, lemon, and grape.
Ecomm_Long_Description: White Shark is a sativa-dominant strain that is a cross between Super Skunk, Brazilian, and South Indian. Super Skunk is an indica-dominant strain, while Brazilian and South Indian are sativa-dominant. White Shark shows characteristics from both a sativa and an indica. The flowers are dense, light green and have subtle golden hues. The aroma consists of notes of pine, lemon and complementary grape undertones.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sativa-dominant hybrid with high-THC content and a unique terpene profile.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Pedro's Sweet Sativa is a Canadian-bred cross of a Dominican sativa with White Russian and an unknown indica. The result is a sativa-dominant hybrid that produces large, airy flowers with high-THC content and a unique terpene profile of humulene, pinene, caryophyllene, and myrcene.

Ecomm_Short_Description: An indica-dominant strain with a strong, sharp pine aroma.
Ecomm_Long_Description: An indica-dominant strain with a strong, sharp pine aroma. Aurora's LA Confidential buds are smaller yet extremely dense and are deep green accented by a medley of red pistil hairs.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sativa-dominant and high-THC boutique strain.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Sativa-dominant, high-THC pre-roll, rolled from a boutique strain called Inverse Square and premium papers.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sativa-dominant and high-THC boutique strain.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Sativa-dominant, high-THC pre-roll, rolled from a boutique strain called Inverse Square and premium papers.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Blend of strawberries and fruit flavours.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Typically dense, sativa-dominant hybrid Vision Qwest (Strawberry Cough, a cross between Strawberry Fields and Haze) has a rich and sprawling variety of phenotypes, ranging from noticeably white to dark purple, with sweet and fruity terpenes. Qwest cannabis is small-batch grown, hand-trimmed, and top cut to attain the densest and most robust flower.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Fruity aroma and a smooth creamy flavour.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Ice Qwest (a Wedding Cake and Gelato cross) is a sweet and fruity indica-dominant strain. Qwest cannabis is small-batch grown, hand-trimmed, and top cut to attain the densest and most robust flower.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Creamy taste with subtle spice flavours.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Spirit Qwest (Wedding Breath, a cross between Wedding Cake and Mendo Breath) is a rare indica-dominant strain with a grape profile and a flower structure akin to the renowned Purple Haze. Qwest cannabis is small-batch grown, hand-trimmed, and top cut (to attain the densest and most robust flowers).

Ecomm_Short_Description: Aromatic zesty citrus and subtly sweet flavours.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Sativa-dominant Super Lemon Haze strain (Zest Qwest), combining  favoured genetics from popular parent strains Lemon Skunk and Super Silver Haze, Super Lemon Haze has a frosty layer of kief bearing a blonde tint. Naturally lanky flowers feature signature aromatics of zesty citrus. Qwest cannabis is small-batch grown, hand-trimmed, and top cut (to attain the densest and most robust buds).

Ecomm_Short_Description: Hint of pine, and sweet and sour undertones.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Wonder Qwest (Sour Diesel, a cross between Chemdawg91 and Super Skunk) has a rare flavour profile that matches its name. Fluffy with resinous white-hued sugar leaves, it is truly sour with sweet hints of citrus. Pungent and tart, this is a hearty phenotype that is small-batch grown, hand-trimmed, and top cut (to attain the densest and most robust flowers).

Ecomm_Short_Description: Robust and full-bodied musky aroma with earthy terpenes.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Escape Qwest (Death Bubba, a cross between Bubba Kush and Death Star) is cultivated using the mineral rich soils and streams of the Pacific Northwest. A heavy indica, Death Bubba presents a robust flower structure, which yields earthy terpenes of wood and pine. With bright pistils and bulbous trichomes, Death Bubba has a familiar musk reminiscent of other BC-grown favourites.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sour, vintage cheese aroma with a floral, pine aftertaste.
Ecomm_Long_Description: This sativa-dominant hybrid is a cross between Skunk #1 and Afghani strains. It has a light green flower that produces a sour smelling, vintage cheese aroma and has a floral, pine aftertaste.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Notes of sweet berry paired with an earthy floral aroma.
Ecomm_Long_Description: An indica-dominant flower from Shishkaberry lineage with mid-to-high THC levels and notes of sweet berry paired with an earthy floral aroma.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sweet earthy pine scent with notes of lemon and pepper.
Ecomm_Long_Description: No 501. Shooting Star is also known as Jack Herer, which is named after a famed cannabis activist, and has a sweet earthy pine scent with notes of lemon and pepper.

Ecomm_Long_Description: Indica-dominant mid-to-high THC flower from a White Widow lineage. Known for its potential to produce a thick layer of trichomes, White Light typically presents rich earthy, citrus, and pine aromas.

Ecomm_Long_Description: No 501. Shooting Star is also known as Jack Herer, which is named after a famed cannabis activist, and has a sweet earthy pine scent with notes of lemon and pepper.

Ecomm_Short_Description: An indica-dominant strain with a piney, spicy aroma.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Shishkaberry is an indoor-grown indica-dominant strain with mid-range THC potency. It has a piney, spicy taste. DJ Short Blueberry and Afghani Kush are parent strains.

Ecomm_Short_Description: This balanced oral spray made from hybrid strains is blended with MCT oil.
Ecomm_Long_Description: This ingestible oral spray uses a blend of hybrid strains and is made with non-GMO, coconut-derived MCT oil. It has a balanced THC:CBD ratio, with 1 milligram of each cannabinoid per spray. (There are 200 sprays per bottle).

Ecomm_Short_Description: Balanced strain with a hoppy, fruity, and citrusy taste.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Balanced Riverview Ride is an indica-dominant strain from God Cross Bud lineage that has nearly equal levels of THC and CBD. It has a hoppy, fruity, and citrusy taste.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Multi-LP pack of five 1g samples of indica, sativa, and hybrid flower.
Ecomm_Long_Description: A multi-LP discovery pack containing five 1g samples from different licensed producers. Each 1g sample is individually packaged and then packaged within a single box. The Discovery Series Vol. 1 - Multi-Pack includes sativa-dominant  Rio Bravo (Wabanaki) from Edison Cannabis Co, Saturday's sativa-dominant CBD MediHaze, Symbl's hybrid Solar Power (Sour Kush), Haven St's indica-dominant No 405 (Blueberry Kush) and 7ACRES's  indica-dominant Sensi Star.

Ecomm_Short_Description: A piney, indica-dominant strain with high-THC content.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Cold Creek Kush is an indica-dominant strain with high-THC content that has an herbal, earthy, piney and woody taste. It is a cross between MK Ultra and Chemdawg91.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sweet and sour taste with notes of kiwi and citrus.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Atomical Haze is an 80/20 sativa-dominant strain propagated by the THC BioMed's growing team. This haze is a combination of Indian Haze and Sweet Afghan. The flowers are a shiny dark green with deep amber hairs. This strain has a sweet and sour taste that is distinctly haze with a few notes of kiwi and citrus. These flowers are hand-trimmed from plants grown naturally in soil, using organic methods.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Potent strain with a strong floral aroma and notes of grape.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Bred to provide a unique sativa strain, this premium flower presents hues of sandy browns and lighter greens that contain colourful bursts of amber hairs. This THC BioMed proprietary strain has a very potent floral aroma, with subtle notes of grape and melon. This flower is  hand-trimmed from plants that are grown naturally in soil using organic methods.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Indica with an earthy aroma and a hint of berries.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Bred to deliver a unique indica strain. This THC BioMed proprietary strain's premium flowers are dark green in colour with amber hairs and carry a heavy dusting of THC crystals. This strain brings earthy and grassy notes with hints of blackberries. This flower is hand-trimmed from plants grown naturally in soil using organic methods.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Earthy and sweet with flavours of nectarine, pepper, and honey cream.
Ecomm_Long_Description: This THC BioMed proprietary strain has been bred to deliver a balanced hybrid with high THC levels. These premium flowers are light green with contrasting deep orange hairs and a heavy dusting of THC crystals. This strain combines smells that are both earthy and sweet, with flavours of nectarine, pepper and honey cream. These flowers are hand-trimmed from plants grown naturally in soil, using organic methods.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Spicy and warm aroma with hints of clove and delicate floral notes.
Ecomm_Long_Description: This THC BioMed proprietary strain has been bred to provide a balanced CBD indica strain with high levels of CBD. These premium flowers are covered in deep amber hairs and a variety of dark greens, yellows, and specks of brown. This strain brings a very spicy and warm aroma with hints of clove and delicate floral notes. These buds are hand trimmed from plants grown naturally in soil, using organic methods.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-CBD softgel capsules with MCT oil base.
Ecomm_Long_Description: These mild softgels are produced by extracting Aurora's CBD strains to the optimal concentration in ultra-pure MCT oil. The extract is then added to size-0 softgels.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Ingestible THC oil with an MCT base.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Broken Coast Cannabis THC Oil is made from a custom blend of THC strains. The cannabis is infused into an MCT carrier oil and decarboxylated (activated) to create an ingestible oil that can be taken sublingually or added to food.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Blend of strawberry and fruit flavours.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Typically dense, sativa-dominant hybrid Vision Qwest (Strawberry Cough, a cross between Strawberry Fields and Haze) has a rich and sprawling variety of phenotypes, ranging from noticeably white to dark purple, with sweet and fruity terpenes. Qwest cannabis is small-batch grown, hand-trimmed, and top cut to attain the densest and most robust flower.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Pre-roll with lemon and pine aromas.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Sativa-dominant strain with a lemon and pine aroma that comes from prominent pinene and humulene terpenes. This mid THC strain comes from a Nigerian Hasplant and Lemon OG Kush lineage. Available as a one gram pre-roll.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Hint of pine, with sweet and sour undertones.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Wonder Qwest (Sour Diesel, a cross between Chemdawg91 and Super Skunk) has a rare flavour profile that matches its name. Fluffy with resinous white-hued sugar leaves, it is truly sour with sweet hints of citrus. Pungent and tart, this is a hearty phenotype that is small-batch grown, hand-trimmed, and top cut (to attain the densest and most robust flowers).

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC strain with sweet, earthy, and diesel aromas.
Ecomm_Long_Description: High-THC, indica-dominant strain from Rockstar lineage with complex sweet, earthy, and diesel aromas.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC hybrid with peppery and floral terpenes.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Headband is a high-THC, sativa-dominant hybrid that is a cross of OG Kush and Sour Diesel. Flowers are compact and relatively uniform. The terpenes found in this Headband strain include nerolidol, which is commonly found in jasmine and lavender, and caryophyllene, which can be found in black pepper and cloves.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Strong pine notes and subtle lemon undertones.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Indica-dominant hybrid with a strong aroma consisting of strong pine notes and subtle lemon undertones. Ultra is a cross between OG Kush and G13.

Ecomm_Long_Description: Hybrid of a Skunk and Afghani cross with sweet and sour aromas from the combination of terpenes such as pinene, caryophyllene, limonene and myrcene.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC strain with hints of lemon and pine.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Frosted dark green leaves hide pastel flowers loaded with golden crystal trichomes. Hints of lemon and pine come through in Jean Guys flavour.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Balanced CBD and THC strain with piney, citrusy and musky aromas.
Ecomm_Long_Description: With an equal balance of CBD to THC, Amnesia's prominent terpenes include pinene, limonene, and myrcene - giving it a piney, citrusy, and musky aroma. This strain is also known as Harmonic.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-CBD strain with floral notes.
Ecomm_Long_Description: A rare, pure CBD strain with bold floral scents, sativa-dominant North Star contains 13.5-16% CBD.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-CBD strain with floral notes.
Ecomm_Long_Description: A rare, pure CBD strain with bold floral scents, sativa-dominant North Star contains 13.5-16% CBD.

Ecomm_Long_Description: Made from 7ACRES' Sensi Star strain, this high-THC, indica-dominant oil has a pungent, gassy, lemon and pepper aroma. Sensi Star's terpene expression is preserved in this CO2-extracted oil, made with MCT oil. It contains 27.2 milligrams of THC and 0.8 milligrams of CBD per millilitre.

Ecomm_Short_Description: A high-THC, sativa-dominant hybrid with sweet, fruity aromas.
Ecomm_Long_Description: A high-THC, sativa-dominant hybrid (Skunk #1 crossed with Afghani) with sweet, fruity aromas. The dense, lime green flowers coated in resin create an earthy, pungent aroma. It offers well-balanced terpenes such as beta-caryophyllene and beta-pinene.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-CBD, low-THC strain from Cannatonic lineage.
Ecomm_Long_Description: High-CBD, low-THC strain from Ruderalis and Cannatonic lineage, bred by Resin Seeds. Piney and earthy flavours come from the dominant terpenes pinene and caryophyllene.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC, indica-dominant hybrid with sour, piney notes.
Ecomm_Long_Description: High-THC, indica-dominant hybrid (MK Ultra and Chemdawg 91) that is the work of breeder T.H Seeds. The sour and piney aromas come from dominant terpene in this variety is beta-pinene.

Ecomm_Short_Description: A combo pre-roll pack (2) with one sativa and indica strain.
Ecomm_Long_Description: A combo pack of strains. Cold Creek Kush (MK Ultra crossed with Chemdawg91) is an indica-dominant hybrid with sour and piney aromas, while Green Cush (Skunk #1 crossed with Afghani) is a sativa-dominant strain with a sweet and fruity forward aroma similar to mango.

Ecomm_Short_Description: A high-THC, sativa-dominant hybrid with sweet, fruity aromas.
Ecomm_Long_Description: A high-THC, sativa-dominant hybrid from Skunk #1 and Afghani lineage. Its resin-coated limey green flowers create an earthy pungent aroma and a sweet fruity, mango flavour.

Ecomm_Short_Description: A high-THC, sativa-dominant hybrid with sweet, fruity aromas.
Ecomm_Long_Description: A high-THC, sativa-dominant hybrid from Skunk #1 and Afghani lineage. Its resin-coated limey green flowers create an earthy pungent aroma and a sweet fruity, mango flavour.

Ecomm_Long_Description: A hybrid of two classic genetics, Jack Herer and NY Diesel. This strain is grown in a state-of-the-art facility to expand its potency and terpene profile. BC Diesel is hand-trimmed and craft cured.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Spicy sweet citrus and fruity herbal tea aromas.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Spicy sweet citrus and fruity herbal tea aromas. Flowr's BC Durga Mata is a unique indica-dominant strain that originated in South Asia. Grown in an indoor facility in Kelowna, this product is hand-trimmed and craft-cured.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Spicy sweet citrus and fruity herbal tea aromas.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Spicy sweet citrus and fruity herbal tea aromas. Flowr's BC Durga Mata is a unique indica-dominant strain that originated in South Asia. Grown in an indoor facility in Kelowna, this product is hand-trimmed and craft-cured.

Ecomm_Short_Description: A sativa-dominant hybrid containing medium amounts of THC.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Bella donna means beautiful lady in Italian. This sativa-dominant hybrid contains medium amounts of THC and emits an unmistakable fruity scent with a lingering aftertaste of spice and mint. Flowers are dense and compact with dark and light green colours combined with brown and red pistils. This 'beautiful lady' has been grown in BC and expertly cured. Super Skunk is a parent strain.

Ecomm_Short_Description: A sativa-dominant hybrid containing low to medium amounts of THC.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Bella donna meaning beautiful lady in Italian describes the BC Belladonna strain perfectly. A sativa-dominant hybrid containing low to medium amounts of THC, it emits an unmistakable fruity scent and with lingering aftertaste of spice and mint. Buds are dense and compact with dark and light green colours combined with brown and red pistils. Flowr's BC Belladonna has been handled with care, grown in BC and expertly cured. Super Skunk is a parent strain.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Complex sativa-dominant variety containing a medium amount of THC.
Ecomm_Long_Description: With its genetic origins being slightly mysterious, Flowr's BC Spoetnik is thought to have strong Afghani traits. With earthy aromas and hints of fruitiness, this is a complex and interesting variety containing a medium amount of THC and no CBD. This product is craft grown in BC and hand-trimmed to emphasize its rich, dark green flowers.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Complex sativa-dominant variety containing a medium amount of THC.
Ecomm_Long_Description: With its genetic origins being slightly mysterious, Flowr's BC Spoetnik is thought to have strong Afghani traits. With earthy aromas and hints of fruitiness, this is a complex and interesting sativa-dominant variety containing a medium amount of THC and no CBD. This product is craft grown in BC and hand-trimmed to emphasize its rich, dark green flowers.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Kent County Kush is a high-THC, indica-dominant strain.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Kent County Kush (a God Bud cross) is a high-THC, indica-dominant strain with herbacious, citrusy and earthy notes.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sweet and earthy aroma with hints of flowers and citrus fruit.
Ecomm_Long_Description: High-THC, indica-dominant strain from Wappa lineage, with a sweet and earthy aroma, hints of flowers, and citrus fruit scents.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sweet and earthy aroma with hints of flowers and citrus fruit.
Ecomm_Long_Description: High-THC, indica-dominant strain from Wappa lineage, with a sweet and earthy aroma, hints of flowers, and citrus fruit scents.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC strain with an earthy, citrus smell, anda hint of incense.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Master Kush is an indica cross created out of twolandracestrainsfrom different parts of the HinduKush region. Master Kush is bred by the Dutch White Label Seed Company, located in Amsterdam. During maturation the plant produces a subtle earthy, citrus smell witha hint of incense. The taste of Master Kush is reminiscent of hard-rubbed charas hash.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC strain with a sweet aroma balanced with earthy notes.
Ecomm_Long_Description: A hybrid strain whose history is somewhat obscure, but is thought to be from OG Kush lineage, Pink Kush has a high-THC profile and a sweet aroma balanced with earthy notes, thanks to the caryophyllene and limonene in its terpene mix. This indica-dominant strain is grown, hand-trimmed, and hang-dried indoors.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC hybrid with caramel coffee and woodsy pine taste.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Mendocino Purps, or Mendo Purps, or even just The Purps, is a North American indica that comes out of Mendocino County in Northern California. It has medium-thick leaves and green hues that turn purple as the plant ripens. The taste has been likened to caramel coffee and woodsy pine.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Citrusy hybrid with light green flowers and thick orange hairs.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Grown from DNA Genetics Lemon Skunk, this is a citrusy hybrid with light green flowers and thick orange hairs. This 1g pre-roll contains freshly milled flower and high-quality paper.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Cheesy, robust, sweet aroma that is reminiscent of chocolate.
Ecomm_Long_Description: This sativa-dominant THC strain is a well-balanced cross of Exodus UK Cheese and Chocolope. Chocolate Fondue has a complex aroma that is cheesy, robust, sweet, and reminiscent of chocolate.

Ecomm_Long_Description: White Shark is a sativa-dominant cross between Super Skunk x Brazilian x South Indian. The flowers are dense, light green and express subtle golden hues. The aroma consists of notes of pine, lemon and complimentary grape undertones. It contains between 13 and 21 percent THC and less than 2 percent CBD.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sativa-dominant, mid-to-high THC strain with citrus notes.
Ecomm_Long_Description: A mid-to-high THC, sativa-dominant strain from a lineage of Las Vegas Lemon Skunk and Zkittlez. Bright green flowers have a tinge of yellow, accompanied by a raw citrus taste and rich lemon aroma. Lemon Zkittle is a split of 60% sativa and 40% indica.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Hybrid milled flower pre-roll with spicy notes.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Crafted from milled hybrid flower that comes from a lineage of Critical Kush and Blue Dream and has spicy notes, these cone-shaped, 0.5-gram joints come packaged in child-resistant, single-unit packaging.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC strain (Chemdawg) with a robust, earthy, spicy aroma.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Houseplant Sativa is a high-THC strain (Chemdawg) from OG Kush and Sour Diesel lineage. This plant has dark, hardy leaves and strong resin production-its long, densely packed trichomes extend from the flowers onto the adjacent leaves, giving it a true "sugar leaf" appearance. Caryophyllene and myrcene, the two most dominant terpenes, give Houseplant Sativa its robust, earthy, spicy aroma.

Ecomm_Long_Description: Ghost Train Haze  is a sativa-dominant hybrid strain that is high in THC. Its ancestry can be traced back to Thailand, Colombia, Mexico and the US. As indicated by the name, aromas are sour and hazy. It contains between 14 and 19 percent THC and less than 1 percent CBD.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Ultra Sour is a high-THC sativa-dominant strain.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Ultra Sour is a high-THC sativa-dominant strain. A cross between MK Ultra and East Coast Sour Diesel, it has a sour taste and an aroma of minty, earthy flavours. Flowers are deep green in colour with organe pistils and contain  between 15 and 25 percent THC, with less than 2 percent CBD.

Its lineage is Shark Shock (a cross between White Widow and Skunk #1 by Dinafem Genetics) bred by CBD Crew to produce a unique, high-CBD variant of the classic Shark Shock strain.

This strain showcases a complex and pungent aroma profile of diesel, citrus, and fennel. Hand-trimmed in the Okanagan to preserve maximum trichome retention.

Ecomm_Long_Description: Wappa is an indica-dominant strain featuring frosty, vibrant lime-coloured buds and a sweet, fruity aroma. Wappa contains between 10 and 20 percent THC and less than 1 percent CBD.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC strain with a sweet berry/fruity aroma.
Ecomm_Long_Description: High-THC strain with a sweet berry/fruity aroma from Blueberry genetics and Glueberry OG lineage. This strain features OG Kush aromas and Gorilla Glue potency.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Mid-THC strain with earthy moss and sweet citrus undertones.
Ecomm_Long_Description: NYC Diesel has solidly dense, grassy green flowers and a very thick layer of bright orange pistils, topped with a noticeable coating of trichomes for a frost-tipped appearance. This classic mid-THC, sativa-dominant hybrid strain is known for its sharp diesel aroma accompanied by traces of earthy moss and sweet citrus undertones, and a distinct flavour of exotic red grapefruit and tart lemon.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Wappa is an indica-dominant strain with a sweet, fruity aroma.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Wappa is an indica-dominant strain featuring frosty, vibrant lime-coloured buds and a sweet, fruity aroma. Wappa contains between 10 and 20 percent THC and less than 1 percent CBD.
