Ecomm_Long_Description: Balanced hybrid blend with equal levels of CBD and THC, and earthy, piney notes.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Herbal-scented hybrid with a balance of CBD and THC.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Prepared using the freshly milled flower of the dense Penelope strain, which is a herbal-scented hybrid with a balance of CBD and THC (from CBD Skunk Haze lineage).

Ecomm_Short_Description: Blueberry aroma with hints of spice and pine.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Sky Pilot is a sweet and pungent strain selected exclusively by Tantalus Labs from a Blue Dream cross. Named after the prominent Sky Pilot peak in the Tantalus Mountain Range, this high-THC strain features large flowers with an ultra-frosted appearance. Featuring the scent of blueberry with hints of spice and pine.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Blueberry aroma with hints of spice and pine.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Sky Pilot is a sweet and pungent strain selected exclusively by Tantalus Labs from a Blue Dream cross. Named after the prominent Sky Pilot peak in the Tantalus Mountain Range, this high-THC rotating strain features large flowers with an ultra-frosted appearance. Featuring the scent of blueberry with hints of spice and pine.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Herbal and earthy nose with notes of pine.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Kali Mist comes from unknown lineage that has given it sativa growth and flowering formation. This flower is medium in size and vibrant green, with bright orange hairs and high trichome coverage. There is a herbal and earthy nose with notes of pine.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC strain with sweet citrus and pine undertones.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Island Honey is a high-THC, sativa-dominant strain. The dense, angular flowers give off a distinct sweet aroma, true to its name, with citrus and pine undertones. Dark green leaves with deep orange hairs have a healthy dusting of trichomes.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC strain with strong aromas of wood, earth, and pine.
Ecomm_Long_Description: White Rhino is a high-THC cross between White Widow and Afghani genetics. Its large, resinous flowers produce strong aromas of wood, earth and pine. It is a heavy indica with dominant pinene, caryophyllene, and myrcene terpenes. White Rhino has green and purple leaves that are coated with clear, dense trichomes.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sativa-dominant strain with smell and taste of fresh Florida oranges.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Sativa-dominant, mid-to-high-THC strain from Agent Orange lineage. A unique terpene profile gives this strain its most distinctive quality-the smell and taste of fresh Florida oranges.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sativa-dominant strain with smell and taste of fresh Florida oranges.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Sativa-dominant, mid-to-high-THC strain from Agent Orange lineage. A unique terpene profile gives this strain its most distinctive quality-the smell and taste of fresh Florida oranges.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Musty lemon aromas and piney, peppery notes.
Ecomm_Long_Description: High-THC strain with musty lemon aromas and piney, peppery notes.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Herbal and earthy nose with notes of pine.
Ecomm_Long_Description: This Kali Mist's parents are unknown, but the plant has a sativa style growth and flowering formation. This bud is medium in size and vibrant green, with bright orange hairs in colour and high trichome coverage. This strain has a herbal and earthy nose with notes of pine.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Hybrid, high-THC strain with an earthy, woodsy aroma of fresh pine.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Indigo Daze (Sensi Star) is a hybrid, high-THC strain that has a powerful aroma of fresh pine followed by earthy and wood undertones.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC strain with notes of sweet citrus and fresh black pepper.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Sapphire Daze (Shishkaberry) is an indica-dominant, high-THC strain with medium size flowers that are bright green with brown hair and a coating of trichomes. This strain presents a powerful sweet citrus and fresh black pepper aroma.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC strain with musty lemon aromas and piney, peppery notes.
Ecomm_Long_Description: High-THC, sativa-dominant strain from Rascal OG lineage with strong musty lemon aromas and notes of pine and pepper.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC strain with fresh pine aromas and earthy undertones.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Indigo Daze (Sensi Star) is a hybrid, high-THC strain that has a powerful aroma of fresh pine followed by earthy and wood undertones.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC flower with sweet notes of vanilla and berries.
Ecomm_Long_Description: High-THC flower from Pink Kush lineage. Haven St. No. 418 Big Dipper may feature sweet notes of vanilla and berries with underlying floral tones.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC strain with sweet notes of vanilla and berries.
Ecomm_Long_Description: High-THC flower from Pink Kush lineage. Haven St. No. 418 Big Dipper features sweet notes of vanilla and berries with underlying floral tones.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Earthy and woodsy aroma with flowery undertones.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Haven St. No. 419 Couch Surf is a mid-to-high-THC hybrid from Afghani Kush lineage. It has an earthy and woodsy aroma with flowery undertones.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Earthy and woodsy aroma with flowery undertones.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Haven St. No. 419 Couch Surf is a mid-to-high-THC hybrid from Afghani Kush lineage. It has an earthy and woodsy aroma with flowery undertones.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Peat-like earthy tones with sharp lemon and fuel aromas.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Haven St. No. 415 Crimson Sky (Cowboy Kush) is a mid-to-high-THC indica-dominant strain that has sharp, sweet, tart, and astringent aromas that may provide light peat-like earthy tones with sharp lemon and fuel scents.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Herbal notes with earthy, woody, and sour pine aromas.
Ecomm_Long_Description: High-THC Haven St. No. 416 Cosmic Thunder (Cold Creek Kush) may present strong herbal notes with earthy, woody, and sour pine tones.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC spicy citrus followed by diesel and earthy notes.
Ecomm_Long_Description: High-THC Haven St. No. 509 Skyscraper (Shishkaberry) may have a pungent aroma of spicy citrus followed by diesel and earthy notes.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Fifteen softgel capsules with 10mg THC and trace of CBD each.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Houseplant Sativa Softgels are made using non-GMO, coconut derived MCT oil and pure cannabis extract.

Ecomm_Short_Description: An indica-dominant strain with a strong, sharp pine aroma.
Ecomm_Long_Description: An indica-dominant strain with a strong, sharp pine aroma. Aurora's LA Confidential buds are smaller yet extremely dense and are deep green accented by a medley of red pistil hairs.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC strain with a chocolate aroma.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Chocolope is a potent high-THC sativa-dominant strain with a sweet chocolate taste and a prominent myrcene terpene profile.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Fifteen softgel capsules with 20mg of THC each in MCT carrier oil.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Each Tweed CBD Softgel is made using non-GMO, coconut-derived MCT oil. Each package contains 15 capsules.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Orange-haired flowers with sweet, floral, and fruity aromas.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Sweet melon, spicy, floral, and fruity aromas come from the terpenes myrcene (found in hops, lemongrass, and mangoes), pinene (found in pine needles, rosemary, and basil) and caryophyllene (found in black pepper, cloves, and oregano).

Ecomm_Short_Description: White-haired flowers with pungent, sour, and citrusy aromas.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Pungent, sour, and citrus aromas come from the terpenes myrcene (found in hops, lemongrass, and mangoes), limonene (found in lemons, limes, and oranges), and caryophyllene (found in black pepper, cloves, and oregano).

Skunky, funky, and sour, this frosty, hand-trimmed, indica-dominant strain is known for its peppery, piney, and sour aromas that come from the strains myrcene, caryophyllene, and limonene terpene profile.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC hybrid pre-roll with frosty hand-trimmed flowers.
Ecomm_Long_Description: High-THC hybrid with frosty hand-trimmed flowers. Aroma of a pine forest blooming with flowers come from the strains myrcene, caryophyllene, and linalool terpene profile.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC, indica-dominant Hindu Kush strain.
Ecomm_Long_Description: The Bakerstreet cultivar is an indica-dominant, high-THC strain (Hindu Kush). Its dense and deep green flowers are highlighted with ochre-hued pistils and covered with trichomes. Terpinolene is the terpene that gives this strain its scent of juniper.

Sweet, sour, piney, and fruity aromas come from the terpenes myrcene (found in hops, lemongrass, and mangoes), limonene (found in lemons, limes, and oranges) and caryophyllene (found in black pepper, cloves, and oregano).

Ecomm_Short_Description: Blend of whole THC flower.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Categorized by potency rather than cultivar, this blended whole flower features moderate levels of THC.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Blend of whole flower with 10-16% THC.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Categorized by potency rather than cultivar, this blended whole flower features between 10-16% THC.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Long dense flowers with peppery and savoury herb notes.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Blast Off flowers are long, but dense and solid, with variations in leaf colour that range from deep emerald green to a dusty sage. Along with pronounced trichome coverage, the appearance is balanced by thick tendrils of brick-red pistils. Caryophyllene brings flavours of pepper and savoury herbs.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Blend of whole flower with 10-16% THC.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Categorized by potency rather than cultivar, this blended whole flower features between 10-16% THC.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Blend of whole flower with 10-16% THC.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Categorized by potency rather than cultivar, this blended whole flower features between 10-16% THC.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sativa-dominant strain from Purple #1 x Skunk lineage.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Given its lineage of Purple #1 x Skunk, Boogie Shoes tends to produce large, tapered flowers that possess an unmistakable purple hue. Its thick leaves are blanketed in trichomes, mixed with delicate orange pistils. Boogie Shoes is rich in myrcene, but its earthy and skunky aromatic profile is balanced with peppery caryophyllene.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Dense flowers with fruity and creamy caramel aromas.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Desfrns flowers tend to be dense and compact, shaped like a serrated pinecone. Its pale green leaves are outlined by a thick ring of milky trichomes and pale amber pistils (hairs). The dominant terpenes in Desfrn include a mix of myrcene, caryophyllene, linalool and pinene, giving it fruity and creamy caramel aromas.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC strain with a sweet citrus and earthy kush smell.
Ecomm_Long_Description: High-THC Master Kush comes from Hindu Kush X Skunk lineage and has tight burnt orange coloured flowers with short ivory pistils (hairs) and a purple hue. Dominant terpenes includepineneandcaryophyllene, which give these flowers a sweet citrus and earthy kush smell.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Spicy and fruity, with flavours similar to pepper and cloves.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Ultimate 2s large and fluffy sage-green flowers are covered with a thick coating of trichomes, offset by clusters of amber pistils (hairs). Spicy and fruity, The Ultimate 2 features caryophyllene, terpinolene and myrcene as its dominant terpenes. Caryophyllene provides flavours similar to pepper, cloves, and caraway.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC strain with aromas of coniferous forest and lemons.
Ecomm_Long_Description: High-THC hybrid strain that grows fat and stout with bushy branches and dark green flowers with orange hairs. Sensi Star has aromas and flavours of a coniferous forest and lemons. These scents and tastes come from limonene and pinene terpenes, which create a unique and pungent aroma that is sometimes considered sweet.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC Orange Bud has aromas of smoky pine and woody citrus.
Ecomm_Long_Description: High-THC Orange Bud showcases thick orange hairs that sprout from elongated, bright green, dense flowers that have a thick coating of sticky trichomes. Orange Bud offers a rich mix of terpenes, the most dominant of which being terpinolene, pinene, caryophyllene, and myrcene. The most abundant terpene in Orange Bud is terpinolene, which gives these flowers their aromas of smoke and pine, complemented by the woody and citrus notes of pinene.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Fruity with peppery and sweet spicy notes.
Ecomm_Long_Description: The Ultimates flowers are large and fluffy, its lime green leaves blanketed with white trichomes, offset by clusters of amber pistils (hairs). Spicy, fresh, and fruity, The Ultimate features caryophyllene, terpinolene and myrcene as its dominant terpenes. Caryophyllene provides flavours similar to pepper, cloves and caraway. Terpinolene evokes flavours closer to other sweet spices such as nutmeg and cumin.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC strain with robust citrus flavour and spicy notes.
Ecomm_Long_Description: High-THC strain with green flowers that feature vibrant orange hues and a frosty layer of trichomes. Creamsicle's high limonene profile gives it a robust citrus flavour, with caryophyllene providing a spicy complement. The flowers are pesticide-free, hand-harvested, and hand-trimmed.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC strain with robust citrus flavour and spicy notes.
Ecomm_Long_Description: High-THC strain with green flowers that feature vibrant orange hues and a frosty layer of trichomes. Creamsicle's high limonene profile gives it a robust citrus flavour, with caryophyllene providing a spicy complement. The flowers are pesticide-free, hand-harvested, and hand-trimmed.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC strain that may present a sour citrus and earthy aroma.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Haven St. No. 401 Jade Sky is a high-THC, indica-dominant strain that may present a sour citrus and earthy aroma.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC strain with diesel, citrus, and fennel aromas.
Ecomm_Long_Description: High-THC, sativa-dominant cross of MK Ultra and East Coast Sour Diesel, which produces large, sticky flowers with pastel hues of greens, yellows, and slightly pinkish pistils. This strain showcases a complex and pungent aroma profile of diesel, citrus, and fennel. Hand-trimmed in the Okanagan to preserve maximum trichome retention.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sweet berry aromas with notes of tart apple and sour grape.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Also known as White Berry, this indica-dominant flower has medium dense, earthy green buds, a plethora of pistils and a thick coating of frosted trichomes. As its name implies, it has a sweet berry aroma balanced out by a bold sourness, and a multi-fruit flavour with plenty of bright blueberry rounded out with hints of tart apple and sour grape. It is a cross between White Widow and Blueberry.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC oil in an MCT carrier oil.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Northern Dew is a high-THC oil blend. The THC comes from a highly concentrated THC distillate combined with a coconut-based MCT carrier oil.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Piney, peppery, and earthy blend.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Mid-to-high-THC sativa blend with piney, peppery, and earthy notes.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-CBD cannabis oil with MCT base.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Pur Dew is a full-spectrum CBD oil made from pure CBD cannabis oil and USDA certified organic MCT coconut oil. Pur Dew has an aromatic smell of cloves, with refreshing hints of citrus and pine.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC oil with an MCT base.
Ecomm_Long_Description: 7ACRES Jean Guy was selected by KKE for its taste and full-bodied aroma. Jean Guy boasts a pungent, citrusy and woody aromatic profile, with a distinct variation of dark and light green colouration. This high-THC oil has an MCT carrier oil base and comes with a separate syringe for oral ingestion.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Fifteen odour-free softgels with 2.5mg of THC and 2.5mg of CBD each.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Solei Balance softgels have no cannabis odour or taste. Each soft gel contains cannabis oil (from Soleil's hybrid greenhouse) paired with MCT oil.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sharp lemon, crisp pine, and warm spice notes.
Ecomm_Long_Description: 7ACRES has developed a sativa-dominant cultivar with a unique combination of sharp lemon, crisp pine, and warm spice notes. 7ACRES Jack Haze was a result of a large genetic selection program, with the goal of finding a novel sativa expression. This particular phenotype stood out among the rest, as it possessed both the sweet haze notes characteristic of a haze cultivar, along with the distinct spice aroma of Jack Herer.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC strain (Muskmelon) from OG Kush lineage.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Saturna (AKA Muskmelon OG from OG Kush lineage) is a high-THC Broken Coast original with an exclusive look, flavour, and aroma.This strain is a result of complicated in-house hybridization with a genetic history unique to Broken Coast. Solid, deep purple flowers feature very large glandular trichomes with a colour that is light but golden.With a unique terpene profile dominated by myrcene, limonene, and caryophyllene, it generates a fruity melon aroma with a musty backbone and notes of gas.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC strain with earthy aromas of pepper, wood, and spice.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Savary (Pink Kush) is a high-THC, indica-dominant hybrid grown in small batches in single strain rooms, then slow cured and hand-trimmed. The solid, trichome covered flowers are bright green with deep purple and orange colours throughout. A dominant terpene profile of caryophyllene, myrcene, and limonene helps to produce earthy aromas of pepper, wood, and spice with a strong earthy, musky flavour profile.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Fifteen softgels with 5mg of CBD and trace of THC each in MCT carrier oil.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Each capsule contains cannabis extract (from a hybrid greenhouse), paired with MCT oil.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC strain (Muskmelon) from OG Kush lineage.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Saturna (AKA Muskmelon OG from OG Kush lineage) is a high-THC Broken Coast original with an exclusive look, flavour, and aroma.This strain is a result of complicated in-house hybridization with a genetic history unique to Broken Coast. Solid, deep purple flowers feature very large glandular trichomes with a colour that is light but golden.With a unique terpene profile dominated by myrcene, limonene, and caryophyllene, it generates a fruity melon aroma with a musty backbone and notes of gas.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Earthy aromas of musk, clove, and peppery citrus.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Stryker (from Rare Dankness No. 2 lineage) is an indica-dominant strain with dense, rounded, frosty flowers with vibrant colouration of deep greens, purples and hints of gold. A dominant terpene profile of myrcene, caryophyllene, and limonene produces pungent earthy aromas of musk, clove, citrus with lemon-pine and peppery notes. This strain creates a heavy diesel and earthy scent.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Notes of citrus and mint with elevated levels of CBG.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Purple Sun God is an indica-dominant cross between Purple God Bud and UBC Chemo, two uniquely West Coast strains. It is bred to feature elevated levels of the lesser-known cannabinoid cannabigerol (CBG). The seaweed-coloured, large and ultra-dense flowers are encased in a thick coat of white trichomes, dotted with light purple hues. Purple Sun God has aromas of tart citrus (ocimene), mint and fennel (pinene), and ylang-ylang (caryophyllene).

Ecomm_Short_Description: Notes of citrus and mint.
Ecomm_Long_Description: A cross between Purple God Bud (a signature 'BC bud') and UBC Chemo, a unique strain developed on the west coast in the 1970s, it is bred to feature cannabigerol (CBG), a cannabinoid of increasing interest. The seaweed-coloured, large and ultra-dense flowers are encased in a thick coat of white trichomes, dotted with light purple hues. Purple Sun God has aromas of tart citrus (ocimene), mint and fennel (pinene) and ylang-ylang (caryophyllene).

Ecomm_Short_Description: Notes of citrus and mint.
Ecomm_Long_Description: A cross between Purple God Bud (a signature 'BC bud') and UBC Chemo, a unique strain developed on the west coast in the 1970s, it is bred to feature cannabigerol (CBG), a cannabinoid of increasing interest. The seaweed-coloured, large and ultra-dense flowers are encased in a thick coat of white trichomes, dotted with light purple hues. Purple Sun God has aromas of tart citrus (ocimene), mint and fennel (pinene) and ylang-ylang (caryophyllene).

Ecomm_Short_Description: Fruity flavours of blueberries and green grapes with hints of mint and cloves.
Ecomm_Long_Description: A classic BC strain, Pure Sunfarms' White Rhino is an indica-dominant child of White Widow. The leaves of this compact bud showcase a variety of colours, ranging from sea green to lime peel, with splashes of amethyst, all nearly hidden beneath a cover of snowy trichomes. It was specifically selected for its sweet and fruity aromas of blueberries and mangos (myrcene), green grapes (alpha-pinene), and Thai basil and cloves (caryophyllene).

Ecomm_Short_Description: Fruity flavours of blueberries and green grapes with hints of mint and cloves.
Ecomm_Long_Description: A classic BC strain, it is a hybrid of White Widow and select cultivars from Brazil and India. The leaves of this compact bud showcase a variety of colours, ranging from sea green to lime peel, with splashes of amethyst, all nearly hidden beneath a cover of snowy trichomes. It was specifically selected for its sweet and fruity aromas of blueberries and mangos (myrcene), green grapes (pinene), and Thai basil and cloves (caryophyllene).

Ecomm_Short_Description: Fruity flavours of blueberries and green grapes with hints of mint and cloves.
Ecomm_Long_Description: A classic BC strain, it is a hybrid of White Widow and select cultivars from Brazil and India. The leaves of this compact bud showcase a variety of colours, ranging from sea green to lime peel, with splashes of amethyst, all nearly hidden beneath a cover of snowy trichomes. It was specifically selected for its sweet and fruity aromas of blueberries and mangos (myrcene), green grapes (pinene), and Thai basil and cloves (caryophyllene).

Ecomm_Short_Description: Herbal and sweet citrus notes of dill, raspberry, and orange sorbet.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Featuring high THC potential, this 'Critical Cut' of Kali Mist is a hybrid of two unknown sativas. Pure Sunfarms' phenotype was grown on the West Coast of British Columbia's Vancouver Island. The tightly-wound, olive green flowers are frosted with sugary trichomes, and showcase aromas of dill and parsley (pinene), raspberry and orange sorbet (myrcene), and oregano (caryophyllene).

Ecomm_Short_Description: Savoury and sweet flavours of cinnamon, honey, and lemon curd.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Created on Vancouver Island by way of the Kootenays, Pure Sunfarms' Island Honey is a cross between a phenotype of Jack Herer from BC's interior, and Early Pearl, a sativa-dominant strain known to thrive in cool climate conditions. Under a carpet of milky trichomes, the leaves range in colour from bright fern to deep emerald green, tangled with delicate amber pistils. It offers notes of sweet spices (caryophyllene), honey (myrcene), and lemon curd (humulene).

Ecomm_Short_Description: Herbal and sweet citrus notes of fresh dill, raspberry, and orange sorbet.
Ecomm_Long_Description: A hybrid of Critical Mass (Afghan x Skunk #1) and Kali Mist, a potent sativa cross of unknown origins, Critical Kali Mist was grown on the west coast of British Columbias Vancouver Island, reportedly inspired by Tofinos surfing community in the 1990s. From large, tightly-wound, olive-green flowers frosted with sugary trichomes, comes aromas and flavours of dill and parsley (pinene), raspberry and orange sorbet (myrcene), and oregano (caryophyllene).

Ecomm_Short_Description: Herbal and sweet citrus notes of fresh dill, raspberry, and orange sorbet.
Ecomm_Long_Description: A hybrid of Critical Mass (Afghan x Skunk #1) and Kali Mist, a potent sativa cross of unknown origins, Critical Kali Mist was grown on the west coast of British Columbias Vancouver Island, reportedly inspired by Tofinos surfing community in the 1990s. From large, tightly-wound, olive-green flowers frosted with sugary trichomes, comes aromas and flavours of dill and parsley (pinene), raspberry and orange sorbet (myrcene), and oregano (caryophyllene).

Ecomm_Short_Description: Savoury flavours of allspice, nutmeg, lavender, lemon, and coriander.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Originating in California, but raised in BC, Pure Sunfarms' Headband is a hybrid of OG Kush and Sour Diesel that became popular in Ontario before finding a home in BC's temperate climate. The dense, elegantly contoured flowers exhibit a range of green colours under a coat of sticky trichomes. It offers savoury flavours of allspice and nutmeg (caryophyllene), lavender (linalool), lemon and coriander seeds (humulene). The combination of these terpenes results in its signature 'gassy' smell.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Savoury flavours of allspice, nutmeg, lavender, lemon, and coriander.
Ecomm_Long_Description: A high-THC cross between a Californian phenotype of OG (Ocean Grown) Kush and Sour Diesel, Headband became popular in Ontario before finding a home on the west coast. The dense, elegantly contoured flowers exhibit a range of green colours under a coat of sticky trichomes. It offers savoury flavours of allspice and nutmeg (caryophyllene, balancing), lavender (linalool), lemon and coriander seeds (humulene). The combination of these terpenes results in its signature gassy smell.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Savoury flavours of allspice, nutmeg, lavender, lemon, and coriander.
Ecomm_Long_Description: A high-THC cross between a Californian phenotype of OG (Ocean Grown) Kush and Sour Diesel, Headband became popular in Ontario before finding a home on the west coast. The dense, elegantly contoured flowers exhibit a range of green colours under a coat of sticky trichomes. It offers savoury flavours of allspice and nutmeg (caryophyllene, balancing), lavender (linalool), lemon and coriander seeds (humulene). The combination of these terpenes results in its signature gassy smell.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sweet and spicy notes of white musk and red peppercorns.
Ecomm_Long_Description: A high-THC heirloom of cultivars that originated in the Hindu Kush mountain region of Central and Southern Asia, Afghan Kush is a building block for many of the Kush varieties available today. The dried flowers are dense, sticky, and chunky - their moss-coloured leaves flecked with shades of purple under a cover of frosty trichomes. It offers aromas and flavours of white musk (myrcene), sandalwood and red peppercorns (caryophyllene), and wild mountain strawberries (linalool).

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sweet and spicy notes of white musk and red peppercorns.
Ecomm_Long_Description: A high-THC cross between strains that originated in the Hindu Kush mountain region of Central and Southern Asia, Afghan Kush is a building block of many of the Kush varieties available today. The dried flowers are dense, sticky and chunky, their moss-coloured leaves flecked with shades of purple under a cover of frosty trichomes. It offers aromas and flavours of white musk (myrcene), sandalwood and red peppercorns (caryophyllene), and wild mountain strawberries (linalool).

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sweet and spicy notes of white musk and red peppercorns.
Ecomm_Long_Description: A high-THC cross between strains that originated in the Hindu Kush mountain region of Central and Southern Asia, Afghan Kush is a building block of many of the Kush varieties available today. The dried flowers are dense, sticky and chunky, their moss-coloured leaves flecked with shades of purple under a cover of frosty trichomes. It offers aromas and flavours of white musk (myrcene), sandalwood and red peppercorns (caryophyllene), and wild mountain strawberries (linalool).

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC hybrid of Super Skunk x Brazilian x South Indian strains.
Ecomm_Long_Description: White Shark is a high-THC cross between Super Skunk x Brazilian x South Indian strains. Super Skunk is an indica dominant strain, while Brazilian and South Indian are sativa dominant, which means White Shark shows both sativa and indica characteristics. The flowers are dense and light green with subtle golden hues.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC blend with a fruity, floral, and spicy aroma.
Ecomm_Long_Description: High-THC blend with a fruity, floral, and spicy aroma. Flowers tend to be dense and a little bit wispy.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Cheesy, robust, sweet aroma that is reminiscent of chocolate.
Ecomm_Long_Description: This sativa-dominant THC strain is a well-balanced cross of Exodus UK Cheese and Chocolope. Chocolate Fondue has a complex aroma that is cheesy, robust, sweet, and reminiscent of chocolate.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sweet and fruity aromas, combined with earthy undertones.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Last Call (MK Ultra) is a high-THC indica-dominant strain made up of light and dark green flowers with fiery amber hairs accented throughout. This strain contains distinct sweet and fruity aromas, combined with earthy undertones.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Citrus aromas with notes of diesel.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Pregame (Ultra Sour) is a sativa-dominant strain with a genetic breakdown of roughly 70% sativa and 30% indica. The strain is made up of light green flowers dusted in a unique layer of white trichomes. It contains citrus aromas and flavours (particularly lemon), with notes of diesel. Its most prominent terpenes are terpinolene, caryophyllene, limonene, andpinene.

Sapphire Daze (Shishkaberry) is an indica-dominant, high-THC strain with medium size flowers that are bright green with brown hair and a coating of trichomes. This strain presents a powerful sweet citrus and fresh black pepper aroma.

Ecomm_Long_Description: Created with a medley of flowers comprised of Aurora's most popular strains, Aurora Aces are made with finely milled whole flower (not trim), rolled in sustainably sourced, vegan-friendly papers.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC hybrid from Captain Krypt-OG and 91 Chemdawg lineage.
Ecomm_Long_Description: High-THC, sativa-dominant hybrid from genetic lineage of Captain Krypt-OG and 91 Chemdawg.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Piney and berry like aromas with a strong kush presence.
Ecomm_Long_Description: This hybrid flower from Gorilla Glue and OG Kush lineage has an elongated structure that is very dense, with light and dark green hues on the bracts and hints of purple. It has piney and berry like aromas that have a strong kush presence.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC strain with smooth berry and citrus aromas.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Hybrid with a zesty, lemon taste.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Lemon Zkittle is a hybrid strain that is the result of crossing Las Vegas Lemon Skunk and Zkittlez strains, which gives it a zesty, lemon taste. The flowers of this strain are a lush green with yellow pistils that are covered in resinous crystals.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC strain with sweet and earthy flavours.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC strain with sweet and earthy flavours.
Ecomm_Long_Description: High-THC, indica-dominant strain from Bubba Kush x Death Star lineage. D.Bubba's flowers are a colourful purple, and have sweet and earthy flavours.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Strong citrus and floral aromas.
Ecomm_Long_Description: This sativa-dominant hybrid from Lime Skunk and Orange Valley OG lineage features strong citrus and floral aromas, giving it an almost lemonade-like quality.

Ecomm_Long_Description: MKLTR (MK Ultra) is an indica-dominant, mid-range THC flower from OG Kush and G13 lineage. The buds have electric amber hairs and flavours of citrus and earth.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Earthy, floral, and musky notes.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Houseplant Indica is selected from a series of unique phenotypes of Kush Origin. Its pungent aroma is complemented with earthy, floral, and musky notes, thanks to the terpenes caryophyllene, linalool, and limonene. Available in multiple formats including various dried flower sizes.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Creamy tropical fruit punch and grape aromas.

This strain has a sweet and sour taste that is distinctly 'haze', with a few notes of kiwi and citrus.

Ecomm_Long_Description: Limelight (Ultra Sour) is a high-THC sativa-dominant strain with tangy, sour, floral notes. Limelights dominant terpenes include caryophyllene, terpinolene, and humulene, and it has a lush flower structure with moss green highlights.

Ecomm_Long_Description: With bright green and yellow flowers, this hybrid strain comes from Las Vegas Lemon Skunk and the Zkittlez lineage. Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC strain with sweet and earthy flavours.
Ecomm_Long_Description: High-THC Pink Kush (from OG Kush lineage) is a unique strain made up of bright green flowers covered in a sugar-like layer of trichomes and pink hairs. Expect sweet and earthy flavours and aromas.

Ecomm_Long_Description: Original Stashs OS.210 is a sativa-dominant hybrid flower blend that delivers earthy, woody, and citrusy aromas through its hero terpene, myrcene. Bouncy and round flowers are a light green colour with dark orange hairs and a heavy dusting of trichomes. Naturally sun grown in hybrid greenhouses, free of synthetic pesticides and insecticides. Available in large 28g (1 ounce) format.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Citrusy orange aromas with subtle earthy and sour tones.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Mimoza has citrusy orange aromas and flavours infused with more subtle earthy and sour tones. It has dense wintergreen flowers with a heavy covering of milky-white trichomes that contrast with hints of orange and purple.

Ecomm_Long_Description: High-THC strain from OG LA Affie and Afghani lineage. Organic certified, hand-raised cannabis grown in living soil without the use of solvents, irradiation, synthetic fertilizers, pesticides or herbicides. Unite Organic is LEED certified and uses eco-friendly packaging.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Earthy and spicy with dominant caryophyllene terpene.

Hand-finished and sorted, with a slow dry and cure, this flower is predominantly lime green, with dark green accents and orange hairs. Its aroma is earthy and spicy with caryophyllene as its most dominant terpene.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sweet and spicy terpene blend.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Helios (Snow Leopard) is a sativa strain that is naturally sun grown in HEXO's hybrid greenhouse located in Gatineau, Quebec with custom feed solutions without the use of synthetic insecticides or pesticides. Hand-finished and sorted, with a slow dry and cure, this large leafy flower is light green in coloration with many orange pistils, and has a sweet and spicy terpene blend.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC hybrid with citrus and earthy aromas.

Hand-finished and sorted, with a slow dry and cure to ensure best possible flavour profiles. Citrus and earthy aromas and flavours stem from the main terpene of myrcene. This round, light green bud has dark orange pistils and an abundance of trichomes.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sweet from its Blueberry lineage, with spicy notes.

Hand-finished and sorted, with a slow dry and cure; this cone-shaped, light green flower has hints of purple colouration with dark orange pistils. The flavour profile is sweet from its Blueberry lineage and has spicy notes.

Hand-finished and sorted, with a slow dry and cure: Nebula's cone-shaped flowers are dark green with hints of purple and light orange pistols. Earthy citrus and spicy pepper notes.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sweet and fruity flavour profile.

Hand-finished and sorted, with a slow dry and cure, this cone-shaped flower has a light green leafy appearance with hints of purple. Featuring a sweet and fruity flavour profile coming from myrcene.

The flower is quite dense with a spade-like shape, dark green leaves, and yellow and orange pistils (hairs). It's coated in a thick layer of trichomes (crystals), that give it an almost yellow glow.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC strain with a strong, sweet, citrus smell.
Ecomm_Long_Description: FIGR No. 17 is a high-THC,  indica-dominant hybrid (Wappa) with a strong, sweet, citrus smell. The flower is quite dense with a spade-like shape, dark green leaves, and yellow and orange pistils (hairs). It's coated in a thick layer of trichomes (crystals), that give it an almost yellow glow.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC strain with a strong, sweet, citrus smell.
Ecomm_Long_Description: FIGR No. 17 is a high-THC,  indica-dominant hybrid (Wappa) with a strong, sweet, citrus smell. The flower is quite dense with a spade-like shape, dark green leaves, and yellow and orange pistils (hairs). It's coated in a thick layer of trichomes (crystals), that give it an almost yellow glow.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Indica cross heavily covered in resin.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Sonora (also known as Stargazer). A cross between starkiller and an unknown indica. Stargazer yields beautiful solid buds with large calyxes, heavily covered in resin. A very frosty purple strain with a dominant terpene profile of limonene, caryophylene, myrcene that creates a unique fruity-gas aroma with a similar dank flavour profile. This indica strain produces thick, heavy smoke and tests medium to high on THC levels with a 70% indica / 30% sativa split.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sativa hybrid with aromas of key lime pie and orange zest.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Denman (also known as Pie in the Sky).  A mostly sativa hybrid this is bright green with perfectly shaped flowers and a nice dusting of trichomes. This strain has one of the most unique and strong terpene profiles of Broken Coasts offerings. Dominant terpenes of Caryophylene, Myrcene and Limonene offer aromas of key lime pie and orange zest, translating into a strong flavour profile. This highly sativa dominant variety is clear with medium THC levels.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Flavours of spice and citrus.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Moresby is a cross between The One and Sannie's Jack resulting in a true sativa, grown the Broken Coast way. The flowers have a sativa-like bud structure with deep purple colouration, lots of frost and orange hairs. A terpene profile creates haze-dominant aromas and flavour profile of spice and citrus.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Tangy, tart aroma with notes of fresh berries.
Ecomm_Long_Description: This sativa-dominant strain (Acadia) produces robust, dense, trichome-frosted flowers, with a tangy, tart aroma and notes of freshly picked field berries.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Woodsy, spicy, and sweet aromas.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Sativa-dominant strain (Wabanaki) that produces compact flowers laced with bright crimson pistils, and features woodsy, spicy, and sweet aromas.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Wappa is an indica-dominant strain with a sweet, fruity aroma.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Wappa is an indica-dominant strain featuring frosty, vibrant lime-coloured buds and a sweet, fruity aroma. Wappa contains between 10 and 20 percent THC and less than 1 percent CBD.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Organic, high-THC strain with strong blueberry aroma.
Ecomm_Long_Description: High-THC BC Organic Blue Dream is a version of the classic sativa dominant strain boasting high THC potency, strong blueberry aromas, and an impressive terpene profile. It's grown in 100% organic, homemade living soil, hand-harvested then cold cured for 14 days before being placed in a fully recyclable glass jar.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Organic, high-THC strain with spicy sandalwood aroma.
Ecomm_Long_Description: This sativa-dominant hybrid is derived from landrace genetics in Africa and then perfected in Robert's Creek on the Sunshine Coast, BC. It's an unusual strain that has a spicy, aromatic sandalwood aroma and medium density flowers with an abundance of red pistils. It's 100% certified organic, grown in homemade living soil, cold cured for 14 days before being placed in a fully recyclable glass jar.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Indica-dominant hybrid with sweet and spicy notes.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Indica-dominant hybrid with sweet and spicy notes. Its small, compact, and berry-like flowers have shades of purple poking through frosty lime-green leaves.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Spicy and sweet with notes of mint.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Big, woolly buds with a rich, spicy aroma; and just a hint of sweet mint on the taste buds are the hallmarks of this high-THC hybrid.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Hints of nutmeg and pepper with a sweet fennel taste.
Ecomm_Long_Description: CALM Twilight (Jager OG) is a spicy indica-dominant strain rich in flavour. The smell has hints of nutmeg and pepper, while the taste is sweet like fennel.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Indica-dominant hybrid with a tropical flavour.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Strawberry Twist (Strawberry Banana) is an indica-dominant hybrid with a tropical flavour.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC, frosty flower.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Frosty, sativa-dominant flower with high levels of THC.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC strain with tangy and sour flavours.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Indica-dominant, high-THC Wedding Cake is from Cherry Pie and GSC lineage. It gets its name from the unmistakable aroma of vanilla cake frosting, but its flavour profile is tangy and sour with a creamy base.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC strain with citrus aroma and sour cherry taste.
Ecomm_Long_Description: High-THC cross of Alien Cookies with a hybrid of Colombian X Starfighter parents, this strain has an aroma of citrus and the taste of sour cherry yoghurt.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC strain with sweet and earthy flavours.
Ecomm_Long_Description: High-THC, indica-dominant strain from Bubba Kush x Death Star lineage. D.Bubba's flowers are a colourful purple, and have sweet and earthy flavours.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC strain with tangy and sour flavours.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Indica-dominant, high-THC Wedding Cake is from Cherry Pie and GSC lineage. It gets its name from the unmistakable aroma of vanilla cake frosting, but its flavour profile is tangy and sour with a creamy base.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Strong citrus and floral aromas.
Ecomm_Long_Description: This sativa-dominant hybrid from Lime Skunk and Orange Valley OG lineage features strong citrus and floral aromas, giving it an almost lemonade-like quality.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sweet notes of grape candy and blueberry muffins.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Purple Punch 2.0 offers complex flavours with a sweet theme. Flowers feature vibrant hues of purple, and a unique aroma similar to that of grape candy and blueberry muffins.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Whole flower pre-rolls with sweet and fruity flavours.
Ecomm_Long_Description: White Rhino single-strain pre-rolls are made with ground whole bud. A child of White Widow, Pure Sunfarms' phenotype was selected for its sweet and fruity flavours of blueberries and mangos (myrcene), green grapes (alpha-pinene), and Thai basil (caryophyllene).  With hemp paper and a bamboo filter, the tapered design offers a twisted end, sealing the joint and acting as a convenient wick.

Ecomm_Short_Description: THC-dominant formula with mango, pineapple, and tropical flavours.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Trailblazer Torches are filled with a highly concentrated CO2 extract, formulated with the sativa-dominant Sparks bold, fresh aroma profile. Compatible with a standard 510-thread battery, Trailblazer Torches are made with stainless steel components, a ceramic atomizer, high-grade glass, and custom mouthpiece. Made with a blend of terpenes, Spark has a mango, pineapple, tropical flavour profile.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Whole flower pre-rolls with herbal and fruity notes.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Critical Kali Mist single-strain pre-rolls are made with ground whole bud. This strain features tightly-wound, olive green flowers frosted with sugary trichomes, and aromas of dill and parsley (pinene), raspberry and orange sorbet (myrcene), and oregano (caryophyllene). With hemp paper and a bamboo filter, the tapered design offers a twisted end, sealing the joint and acting as a convenient wick.

Ecomm_Short_Description: THC-dominant formula with grape and blueberry flavours.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Trailblazer Torches are filled with a highly concentrated CO2 extract, formulated with the indica-dominant Flicker's bold, fresh aroma profile. Compatible with a standard 510-thread battery, Trailblazer Torches are made with stainless steel components, a ceramic atomizer, high-grade glass, and custom mouthpiece. Made with a blend of terpenes, Flicker has a grape and blueberry flavour profile.

Ecomm_Short_Description: THC-dominant formula with cherry flavour and sour, earthy notes.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Trailblazer Torches are filled with a highly concentrated CO2 extract, formulated with the hybrid Glow's bold, fresh aroma profile. Compatible with a standard 510-thread battery, Trailblazer Torches are made with stainless steel components, a ceramic atomizer, high-grade glass, and custom mouthpiece. Made with a blend of terpenes, Glow has a flavour profile of sour and earthy tones with notes of cherry.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Disposable vape with notes of lemon, pine, and herbs.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Edison + Feather ready-to-use vape pens are inhalation-activated and contain cannabis distillate and the sativa-dominant Rio Bravos (Wabanaki) aroma profile. Rio Bravos 'True-to-Flower' flavour of lemon, pine, and herbs is captured in this tailored formulation with a precise botanical blend of dominant terpenes, including terpinolene, caryophyllene, myrcene, and pinene.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Disposable vape with floral, sweet, and berry notes.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Edison + Feather ready-to-use vape pens are inhalation-activated and contain cannabis distillate and the sativa-dominant La Strada's (Acadia) aroma profile. La Strada's 'True-to-Flower' floral and sweet flavour with berry notes is captured in this tailored formulation with a precise botanical blend of dominant terpenes, including pinene, caryophyllene, myrcene, and humulene.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC strain with spicy, citrusy, and fresh flavours.
Ecomm_Long_Description: High-THC Lemon Zkittle is a pungent sativa with complex notes of spicy caryophyllene, citrusy limonene, and fresh linalool. Buds are bright green and yellow crystal covered.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Piney strain with woody and citrus notes.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Orange Bud showcases thick orange hairs that sprout from elongated, bright green, dense buds. It also boasts a generous coating of sticky trichomes. Orange Bud offers a rich mix of terpenes with aromatic nuances of smoke and pine, complemented by woody and citrus notes.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sparkling lemon & lime beverage with 10mg of CBD.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Everies lemon & lime sparkling beverage is lightly sweetened and bursting with citrus flavour. Infused with 10mg of CBD. Contains small amounts of THC. Best served chilled or over ice.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sparkling dragon fruit and watermelon beverage with 10mg of CBD.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Everie's Dragon Fruit Watermelon Sparkling Beverage is a blend of tropical flavours with a touch of sweetness. Infused with 10mg of CBD. Contains small amounts of THC. Best served chilled over ice.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Mango passionfruit sparkling beverage infused with 10mg of CBD.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Everies Mango Passionfruit Sparkling Beverage is a balance of sweet and tart fruit flavours. Infused with 10mg of CBD. Contains small amounts of THC. Best served chilled or over ice.

Ecomm_Short_Description: THC-dominant strain.
Ecomm_Long_Description: THC-dominant strain from a selection of indica with earthy, piney, and peppery notes.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC, pungent and earthy cultivar.
Ecomm_Long_Description: High-THC, BC indica that comes from D. Star and Bubba Kush lineage and is a pungent and earthy cultivar.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC, sweet and earthy strain in PAX Era pod.
Ecomm_Long_Description: West Coast classic cultivar D. Bubba comes in a 0.5ml PAX Era pod. D. Bubba is a high-THC, low-CBD strain that's indica-dominant and has sweet and earthy flavours. Intended for use with a PAX Era device.

Ecomm_Short_Description: THC-dominant concentrate with citrus and floral notes.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Citrique is a THC-dominant sativa-dominant hybrid, with rare genetics and aromas of citrus and floral. For use with a PAX Era only.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sativa-dominant strain with sweet, herbal notes.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Cindy Jack (Cinderella Jack) is a cross between Jack Herer and Cinderella 99. With its dense, green flowers covered with sunset orange pistils and snowy trichomes, this sativa-dominant strain features sweet, herbal notes. Myrcene is the most dominant terpene. However, pinene, caryophyllene, limonene and humulene are also present.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Super-potent, sativa-dominant strain with deep notes of pine and lemony diesel.
Ecomm_Long_Description: From MK Ultra and East Sour Diesel lineage, Ultra Sour is a high-THC, sativa-dominant strain with heavy-hitting citrus and diesel aromas. Using CO2 extraction, and cannabis distillate, the 0.5g PAX Era pod delivers flavour true to the original strain.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Dark, resin-coated buds that provide an earthy, spicy aroma
Ecomm_Long_Description: Blackberry Gum is a cross between Blueberry and Bubble Gum. This strain has dark, resin-coated buds that provide an earthy, spicy aroma, while cotton candy and bubble gum also shine through. It was grown indoors, with minimal human involvement and was harvested by hand at its peak maturity.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Indica-dominant strain with strong sweet-and-spicy aromas.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Northern Lights is a popular descendant of indigenous Afghani Thai landrace strains. It offers up a strong sweet-and-spicy aroma. The buds are dense and coated in crystals. This is an indica-dominant strain. It was grown indoors with minimal human involvement.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Indica-dominant hybrid with fruity, skunk aromas, and hints of mint.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Thin Mint is an indica-dominant hybrid. It delivers a fruity, skunk aroma with hints of mint. It is a cross between Thin Mint Cookies and Green Cr**ck. This flower was grown in Weed Me's indoor clean-room with minimal human involvement, and was harvested by hand at its peak maturity.

Product_Name: GRAND DADDY PURPS X SOUR KUSH DISPOSABLE
Ecomm_Short_Description: THC-dominant formula with notes of berry, grape, and earth.
Ecomm_Long_Description: All-in-one disposable pen with THC-dominant extract from Grand Daddy Purps x Sour Kush lineage. Processed to preserve native terpenes and reintroduce them to the extract to give pungent aromas of berry, grape, and earth.

Product_Name: JEAN GUY X SUPER LEMON HAZE DISPOSABLE
Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC disposable pen with citrus and herbal terpenes.
Ecomm_Long_Description: RIFF's M7 all-in-one pens contain a high potency THC extract and native cannabis terpenes. The CO2 extraction process preserves native terpenes which are reintroduced to THC extract. This process allows users to experience full effects and the natural flavours of cannabis.  The newest duo, Jean Guy and Super Lemon Haze, features an explosion of lemon, citrus, and herbal notes.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Blend with smooth and earthy flavour.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Indica-dominant blend with smooth and earthy flavour.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Iconic cannabis strain in extract form with unmistakable tropical flavour.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Pineapple Express is an iconic cannabis strain with an unmistakable tropical flavour. Now available in extract form, the strain is cured and extracted with C02, purified into distillate, and combined with plant derived terpenes for true-to-flower cannabis flavour. The kit comes with 0.5g Pineapple Express cartridge and 510 lithium battery.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-potency THC extract with earthy, berry, and citrus flavours.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Blue Dreams is high-potency THC extract made from cannabis that is cured then extracted with C02, purified into distillate, and combined with plant derived terpenes to give earthy, berry, and citrus flavours. This kit includes the Blue Dream 0.5g cartridge and a 510 battery.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC formula with lavender, tea, and herbal flavours.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Unplug cartridges have a lavender and tea flavour, with a hint of sweetness and virtually no cannabis after-taste or smell. Unplug cartridges contain high levels of THC and some CBD. They are made with only high-quality, plant-based materials, using distillate cannabis oil extracted from sun-grown cannabis, paired with natural plant-derived terpenes. This kit includes the Unplug 0.5g cartridge and a 510 battery.

Ecomm_Short_Description: 1:1 THC-to-CBD cartridge, battery, and charger.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Balance cartridges have a bright, citrus flavour with notes of lemon and grapefruit, and virtually no cannabis after-taste or smell. The 1:1 THC and CBD formula is made from high-quality, plant-based materials: distillate cannabis oil extracted from sungrown cannabis and natural plant-derived terpenes. This kit includes a cartridge, battery, and charger.

Ecomm_Short_Description: 1:1 THC-to-CBD cartridge, battery, and charger.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Balance cartridges have a bright, citrus flavour with notes of lemon and grapefruit, and virtually no cannabis after-taste or smell. The 1:1 THC and CBD formula is made from high-quality, plant-based materials: distillate cannabis oil extracted from sungrown cannabis and natural plant-derived terpenes. This kit includes a cartridge, battery, and charger.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Inhale-activated battery for 510 thread vape cartridges.
Ecomm_Long_Description: This inhale-activated battery optimizes temperature for a consistent and smooth vapour draw. Compatible with all 510 thread vape cartridges, these batteries are USB rechargeable.

Ecomm_Short_Description: An indica-dominant strain with a strong, sharp pine aroma.
Ecomm_Long_Description: An indica-dominant strain with a strong, sharp pine aroma. Aurora's LA Confidential buds are smaller yet extremely dense and are deep green accented by a medley of red pistil hairs.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Indica-dominant vape cart for use with Luma battery.
Ecomm_Long_Description: High-THC, indica-dominant pods enhanced with ceramic heating technology and featuring a purple mouthpiece for easy identification. Designed for use with Tokyo Smoke's Luma battery.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC hashish from organic-certified cannabis.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Whistler Cannabis Co.'s Hashish is made by hand using a solvent-free, water-based extraction process. It is high in THC, terpene-rich, and is created using organic-certified cannabis.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC, solventless, live rosin.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Created using fresh frozen plant material, not dried, Whistler Cannabis Co's Live Rosin is made using a solventless, water based extraction process. It is high in THC and terpene rich.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC flower with a sour and citrusy aroma.
Ecomm_Long_Description: High-THC cultivar that is half Sour Diesel and half Jack Herer. This hard-to-come by cultivar has leaves the hue of fresh limes, pistils the colour of plump oranges, and an aroma like the smell of sliced lemons. With twinkling trichomes, voluminous buds release the scent of citrus joined by a twang of diesel.  Grown in living soil this quality product is cultivated, rolled and packaged by hand in Whistler, BC. It is packaged using two way humidity control for freshness.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC flower with a sour and citrusy aroma.
Ecomm_Long_Description: High-THC cultivar that is half Sour Diesel and half Jack Herer. This hard-to-come by cultivar has leaves the hue of fresh limes, pistils the colour of plump oranges, and an aroma like the smell of sliced lemons. With twinkling trichomes, voluminous buds release the scent of citrus joined by a twang of diesel.  FVOPA organic certified and grown in living soil this quality product is cultivated, prepared, and packaged by hand in Whistler, BC. It is packaged using two way humidity control for freshness.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sweet strawberry taste with sour notes.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Strawberry Fire OG is an indica-dominant strain that marries Strawberry Cough and Fire OG. This strain produces big, deep green buds tinged with strawberry-blonde hairs. Delicately preserved, crystal-coated flowers offer a sweet yet skunky aroma fuelled by OG lineage. Strawberry Fire OG hits the nose with a sour scent that mutes into a smooth, berry sweetness. This strain packs a fresh flavour, candied sweetness, and strawberry aftertaste.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Zesty notes of citrus, herbs, and pepper.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Sativa-dominant hybrid strain hailing from the GSC lineage crossed with Orange Juice for a tangy, fruity flavour and sour aroma. The buds of this strain are tapered and bright green with fiery orange pistils. Bursting with zesty notes of tangerine and lime, Orange CKS has a citrusy terpene profile, with herbal and peppery notes.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Half-gram pre-roll of Blueberry and Bubble Gum lineage
Ecomm_Long_Description: Blackberry Gum is a cross between Blueberry and Bubble Gum. This strain has dark, resin-coated buds that provide an earthy, spicy aroma, while cotton candy and bubble gum also shine through. The strain was grown indoors, with minimal human involvement and was harvested by hand at its peak maturity.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Indica-dominant strain with strong sweet-and-spicy aromas.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Northern Lights is a popular descendant of indigenous Afghani Thai landrace strains. It offers up a strong sweet-and-spicy aroma. The buds are dense and coated in crystals. This is an indica-dominant strain. It was grown indoors with minimal human involvement.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Fruity, skunk aroma with hints of mint.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Thin Mint is an indica-dominant hybrid that delivers a fruity, skunk aroma with hints of mint. It is a cross between Thin Mint Cookies and GC. This flower was grown in an indoor clean-room with minimal human involvement, and was harvested by hand at its peak maturity.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Floral aroma with woody and earthy notes.
Ecomm_Long_Description: FIGR No. 7 is an Indica dominant (Afghan Kush) strain that originated from the Hindu Kush mountain range near the Afghanistan-Pakistan border. The flavour is reminiscent of a forest clearing filled with wildflowers, with a woody, earthy and sweet floral scent. The plants develop large, sticky, blunt-topped buds and produce large yields.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sweet and fruity sativa-dominant blend.
Ecomm_Long_Description: This sativa-dominant blend is sweet and fruity with loose, airy light green buds.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sweet and fruity sativa-dominant blend.
Ecomm_Long_Description: This sativa-dominant blend is sweet and fruity with loose, airy light green buds.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Ten indica-dominant gel capsules with 5mg of THC each.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Liquid gels are made using an indica blend of whole plant extract, which means that captured terpenes have been recombined with each batch. Each of the 10 capsules contains approximately 5mg of THC and trace amounts of CBD, with an MCT carrier oil.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Ten sativa-dominant gel capsules with 5mg of THC each.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Liquid gels are made using an sativa blend of whole plant extract, which means that captured terpenes have been recombined with each batch. Each of the 10 capsules contains approximately 5mg of THC and trace amounts of CBD, with an MCT carrier oil.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Purple hued buds with a sweet, piney aroma.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Purple-blossomed, indica-dominant Purple Bud, appropriately named for its lavender hues, is a descendant of Afghan Indica and a distant sativa relative from Jamaica (Hindu Kush x Purple Kush lineage). This plant offers large harvests of sparkling buds that carry a sweet, piney aroma.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Purple hued buds with a sweet, piney aroma.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Purple-blossomed, indica-dominant Purple Bud, appropriately named for its lavender hues, is a descendant of Afghan Indica and a distant sativa relative from Jamaica (Hindu Kush x Purple Kush lineage). This plant offers large harvests of sparkling buds that carry a sweet, piney aroma.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Notes of pine, lemon, and grape undertones.
Ecomm_Long_Description: White Shark is a sativa-dominant strain that is a cross between Super Skunk, Brazilian and South Indian. Super Skunk is an indica-dominant strain, while Brazilian and South Indian are sativa-dominant. White Shark shows characteristics from both a sativa and an indica. The buds are dense, light green, and express subtle golden hues. The aroma consists of notes of pine, lemon, and grape undertones.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Notes of pine, lemon, and grape undertones.
Ecomm_Long_Description: White Shark is a sativa-dominant strain that is a cross between Super Skunk, Brazilian and South Indian. Super Skunk is an indica-dominant strain, while Brazilian and South Indian are sativa-dominant. White Shark shows characteristics from both a sativa and an indica. The buds are dense, light green, and express subtle golden hues. The aroma consists of notes of pine, lemon, and grape undertones.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Rich skunky citrus taste and an Afghan-hash aroma.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Critical Orange Punch is a cross between Granddaddy Purps, Orange Bud, and THC-rich Critical. Critical Orange Punch has a rich skunky citrus taste and an Afghan-hash aroma.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Rich skunky citrus taste and an Afghan-hash aroma.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Critical Orange Punch is a cross between Granddaddy Purps, Orange Bud, and THC-rich Critical. Critical Orange Punch has a rich skunky citrus taste and an Afghan-hash aroma.

Ecomm_Short_Description: THC-dominant formula from Lemon Skunk x Florida OG lineage.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Top Leaf vape cartridges are made from ceramic and glass parts, preserving the rich flavour of the full-spectrum extracts. THC-dominant Florida Lemons comes from Lemon Skunk x Florida OG lineage. This cartridge has a 510 thread connection.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sativa-dominant strain from Mango Haze X Lemon Skunk lineage.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Grown indoors in the Okanagan Valley, Delahaze is a sativa-dominant strain from Mango Haze X Lemon Skunk lineage.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC hybrid from OG Kush and Blueberry lineage.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Glueberry OG is a high-THC hybrid that derives from OG Kush and Blueberry lineage.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Flowers feature white pistils and crystal-white trichomes.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Snow Bud is visually identifiable by its white pistils and crystal-white trichomes covered buds. It comes from Afghanistan X Africa lineage.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sativa-dominant strain from Think Different x Power Plant.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Think Fast is a sativa-dominant strain from a cross of Think Different with Power Plant.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC hybrid from various flowers.
Ecomm_Long_Description: High-THC hybrid from various flowers.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Frosty buds with a hint of spice.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Re-Up's WPP (Wappa) has a range of aromas and flavours  including a hint of spice. This strains buds are frosty and lime green, accented by a medley of amber hairs.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC strain with earthy and sweet notes.
Ecomm_Long_Description: High-THC Canadian strain, Nuken is an indica-dominant hybrid (80% indica/20% sativa) strain created as cross between God Bud and Shishkaberry strains. The earthy aroma and taste of Nuken is that of fresh herbs and grass with a hint of sharp skunk and baked marshmallow. Nuken buds have large dense and light minty green buds and sparse fiery orange hairs. Each bud has a fine mixture of cloudy and amber trichomes.

Durga Mata is a 90% indica strain with roots originating in the natural landraces of South Asia. The moss green arrow-shaped buds are speckled with amber hair and coated in a sweet resin from a myriad of crystal trichomes. The earthy, sweet, and citrusy aroma is reminiscent of Italian panettone.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sativa-dominant strain with notes of herb, pine, and diesel.
Ecomm_Long_Description: This sativa-dominant strain is a cross between Dutch Charlotte and Red Angel. Charlotte's Angel features notes of herb, pine, and diesel. This flower was grown in Weed Me's indoor clean-room with minimal human involvement, and was harvested by hand at its peak maturity at their facility in Pickering, ON.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Limelight (Ultra Sour) has tangy, sour, floral notes.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Limelight (Ultra Sour) is a high-THC sativa-dominant strain with tangy, sour, floral notes. Limelight's dominant terpenes include caryophyllene, terpinolene, and humulene, and it's flower includes moss green highlights.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sativa-dominant blend.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Sativa-dominant blend of mid-to-high THC strains.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Indica-dominant blend.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Indica-dominant blend of mid-to-high THC strains.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Balanced CBD/THC topical body cream.
Ecomm_Long_Description: This Extra Strength cream's quick-absorbing formula uses 48North's outdoor grown cannabis. The non-psychoactive formula uses both THC and CBD blended with high-quality natural ingredients (arnica, peppermint, and juniper) and is intended for topical use on the body .

Ecomm_Short_Description: Strong yet sweet aroma that verges on skunkiness.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Machine rolled with a lightweight rolling paper and completed with a paper mouthpiece. Wappa has a strong yet sweet aroma that verges on skunkiness, both of which also come through in the caryophyllene-forward taste profile. This green-and-yellow-coloured indica-dominant strain is greenhouse-grown and pesticide-free.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Citrus and peppery scent accompanied by lemon aftertaste.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Machine rolled with a lightweight rolling paper and completed with a paper mouthpiece. Pre-rolled joints made with White Widow buds. White Widow was developed by The Netherlands Green House Seeds in the 1990s. With its limonene terpenes at work, White Widow has a citrus and peppery scent accompanied by a slight lemon aftertaste.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Musky aroma coupled with a herbal taste profile.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Cold Creek Kush is a hybrid that crosses the powerful MK Ultra with fellow Colorado native Chemdawg 91. The plant has a recognizable dank smell, much like a forest after a rainfall. Its taste profile is strongly herbal and almost overpowering. On the exhale its flavours turn earthy and woody, with a pleasant shock of fresh and sour pine. Cold Creek Kush grows into a tall plant with dense branches covered in thick buds and trichomes.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC cross with notes of cheese.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Sativa-dominant, high-THC cross between Super Haze and Amnesia. Fruity and citrusy notes.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Heavy diesel notes and hints of floral and citrus.
Ecomm_Long_Description: 7ACRES Craft Collective selected this particular Pink Kush for its intensely pungent fuel notes, high-THC levels, and rock-hard density. This is a terpene-rich, indica-dominant hybrid that has an aroma of heavy diesel notes and hints of flowery perfume and citrus. This descendant of OG Kush is small batch, indoor craft-grown in BC. The full plant is hang-dried, hand-trimmed, and masterfully cured. Limited quantities available.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC strain with earthy, black cherry, and liquorice notes.
Ecomm_Long_Description: High-THC Pacific OG is a sativa-dominant hybrid, a Tantalus curation of Goji OG, bred from Nepali OG and Snow Lotus. Nepali OG, aka Nepali Kush, is a long-lineage classic close to Tahoe OG that brings conical-shaped buds and earthy notes of an OG aroma, while Snow Lotus lays an undercurrent of black cherry and subtle hints of liquorice. The colas of Pacific OG are caked, hand-harvested, and cured, providing a full flavour due in part to the terpene profile of limonene, linalool, and myrcene. Contains three 0.5g pre-rolls.

Ecomm_Short_Description: El Dorado is an indica-dominant hybrid with fresh forest notes.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Crafted from milled flower, El Dorado is an indica-dominant hybrid with fresh forest notes and dominant terpenes including pinene and caryophyllene.

Ecomm_Short_Description: El Dorado is an indica-dominant hybrid with fresh forest notes.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Crafted from milled flower, El Dorado is an indica-dominant hybrid with fresh forest notes and dominant terpenes including pinene and caryophyllene.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Single sativa strain with aromas ranging from fresh to fruity.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Full of flavour, each batch of Pure Sunfarms Sativa is chosen to deliver consistent potency and upfront aromatics, from the first flower to the last. Grown in a sunlight-filled, modern greenhouse in British Columbia, the buds are trimmed and hand-groomed, dried and cured with care. Each Sativa pack contains a single strain, with aromas ranging from fresh to fruity.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC strain with a bold, pungent aroma.
Ecomm_Long_Description: DoSi-Pie is a unique, high-THC cross between Do-Si-Dos and Velvet Pie. The result is colourful purple flowers, lime green and violet leaves, shiny trichomes, and a bold, pungent aroma.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Single strain THC-dominant vape cart.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Single cannabis strain Fire OG formulation with purified THC and plant-derived terpenes, made with CO2 extraction. Compatible with a 510-thread battery.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sativa-dominant, single cannabis strain Durban formulation.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Sativa-dominant, THC-dominant, single cannabis strain Durban formulation with purified THC and plant-derived terpenes. Compatible with a 510-thread battery.

Product_Name: BLUE DREAM - VAPE CARTRIDGE AND BATTERY

Ecomm_Short_Description: Rich brown resinous hash made from pressed dry sift.
Ecomm_Long_Description: OS.HASH10 is a pressed, rich brown resinous hash with a firm but pliable feel. Produced from a single hybrid strain, OS.HASH10 is made using dry ice sift trichome extraction and packaged in a 2g format in a resealable, odour-proof and child-resistant pouch.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sharp lemon, crisp pine, and warm spice notes.
Ecomm_Long_Description: 7ACRES has developed a sativa-dominant cultivar with a unique combination of sharp lemon, crisp pine, and warm spice notes. 7ACRES Jack Haze was a result of a large genetic selection program, with the goal of finding a novel sativa expression. This particular phenotype stood out among the rest, as it possessed both the sweet haze notes characteristic of a haze cultivar, along with the distinct spice aroma of Jack Herer.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC sativa strain blend.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Blend of high-THC sativa strains.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Blend of high-THC indica strains.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Blend of high-THC indica strains.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Four seeds from high-THC lemony strain.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Four seeds of a strain that grows tall with flowers coated in resin, and requires a flowering time of 56-63 days. The strain is suitable for both indoor and outdoor growing. Tight, dense buds are rich with bright orange pistils and covered with trichomes that produce sweet and lemony tones.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Earthy aroma with notes of cheese and wood.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Van der Pops Cloudburst is a potent hybrid varietal (UK Cheese) that has an earthy aroma with some notes of cheese and wood.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sativa-dominant cannabis oil cartridge.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Marley Gold vape cartridge is filled with 0.5g of natural, winterized sativa-dominant cannabis oil. The gentle CO2 extraction method means you'll taste the flower's natural aroma and flavour, only milder. Made with CCELL technology and a 510-thread that will fit on most batteries.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Indica-dominant cannabis oil cartridge.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Marley Black vape cartridge is filled with 0.5g of natural, winterized indica-dominant cannabis oil. The gentle CO2 extraction method means you'll taste the flower's natural aroma and flavour, only milder. Made with CCELL technology and a 510-thread that will fit on most batteries.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Organic strain with delicate floral and spicy notes.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Grown using certified-organic practices, and rooted in nutrient-rich living soil, Siren is a high-THC, sativa-dominant hybrid (R2) that carries an aroma of delicate florals, balanced by spicy notes that come from its prominent levels of myrcene. Every ankr jar is composed of recycled materials and a hand-packaged dual-humidity control unit to maintain flower integrity and post-harvest freshness.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Vape cartridge with 1:1 CBD:THC ratio.
Ecomm_Long_Description: The Marley Red CBD-rich vape cartridge is filled with 0.5g of natural cannabis oil - a custom blend formulated with both CBD and THC oils that delivers an approximate 1:1 CBD:THC ratio. The formulation and gentle CO2 extraction means you'll taste the flower's natural aroma and flavour, only milder. Made with CCELL technology and a 510-thread that will fit on most batteries.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Four seeds of Super Lemon Haze.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Four seeds of Super Lemon Haze, which is a kief-caked, multi-coloured plant. Just as the name would suggest it has some lemony characteristics with a zesty, citrusy, aroma accompanied by a tart, sweet like taste that is not as sharp as you may expect. The flowering time is 10 weeks or 70 days and it tends to have an outstanding yield. Large light green buds with lemons and citrus notes.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Four seeds of high-THC hybrid that has citrusy notes.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Four seeds of the high-THC hybrid Pink Lemonade from Pink Kush and Lemon Skunk lineage. This strain smells fruity, with notes of lemon and grapefruit on the exhale. The bud is coated in a generous layer of trichomes atop jade foliage and bronze pistils. It has a flowering period of only seven and a half to eight weeks. Very citrusy aroma, with medium sized tight buds, and great yield.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC blend of carefully selected indica flower.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Featuring a high-THC potential, OS.RESERVE features buds from two rotating, carefully selected indica flower strains that are sungrown in hybrid greenhouses.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Indica-dominant flower with earthy aromas and electric amber hairs.
Ecomm_Long_Description: MKLTR (MK Ultra) is an indica-dominant, mid-range THC flower from OG Kush and G13 lineage. The buds have electric amber hairs and flavours of citrus and earth.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC hybrid with sweet, berry-like aromas.
Ecomm_Long_Description: High-THC Marley Green Blue Dream is a sativa-dominant hybrid with sweet, berry-like aromas.

Ecomm_Short_Description: THC-dominant hybrid with sweet, berry-like aromas.
Ecomm_Long_Description: High-THC Marley Green Blue Dream is a sativa-dominant hybrid with sweet, berry-like aromas.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Piney and earthy tones, with peppery, fruity taste.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Glueberry (Blueberry x Gorilla Glue) is a hybrid of indica and sativa strains with piney and earthy tones, a peppery taste, and a fruity twist.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC strain with sweet hints of sharp sourness.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Ignites GG#4 is grown and hand-crafted by Apollo Green. The high-THC, sativa-dominant strain from Sour Diesel and Sour Dubb lineage, that has a long linage due to the extensive backcrossing of several potent Diesel variants. Buds have been described as being encrusted with diamond-like trichomes with sweet hints of sharp sourness that varies from batch to batch.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Tangy citrus flavour with a finish of rich nutty herbs.
Ecomm_Long_Description: High-THC, Sour Cookies is a phenotype of Mandarin Cookies grown and hand-crafted by Atlas. This is a rare sativa-dominant cookies strain created through the crossing of classic Cookies and Mandarin Sunset. Sour Cookies packs a sharp tangy citrus flavour with a finish of rich nutty herbs upon exhale. The aroma is very earthy and 'kushy' with a sour tangerine overtone that turns slightly pungent when smoked.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC strain with sweet hints of sharp sourness.
Ecomm_Long_Description: Ignite's GG#4 is grown and hand-crafted by Apollo Green. The high-THC, sativa-dominant strain from Sour Diesel and Sour Dubb lineage, that has a long linage due to the extensive backcrossing of several potent Diesel variants. Buds have been described as being encrusted with diamond-like trichomes with sweet hints of sharp sourness that varies from batch to batch.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC strain with sweet, sour, and skunky notes.
Ecomm_Long_Description: High-THC Fireberry Haze is a phenotype of Strawberry Fire OG, grown and hand-crafted by Radicle Cannabis. This sativa-dominant hybrid marries Strawberry Cough and Fire OG. Fireberry produces big, deep green buds highlighted by strawberry-blonde hairs. Delicately preserved, crystal-coated flowers offer a sweet yet skunky aroma fuelled by their OG lineage. Fireberry Haze hits the nose with a sour scent that mutes into a smooth, berry sweetness. This strain packs a fresh flavour of candied sweetness and strawberry.

Ecomm_Short_Description: High-THC indica with a heavy nose.
Ecomm_Long_Description: High-THC Rockstar OG is a handpicked phenotype of Josh D OG, bred by Karma Genetics, grown and hand-crafted by Radicle Cannabis. This potent indica is a three-deep cross ofClassic OGs and Kush with deep green dense buds, thin amber hairs, and a heavy nose.

Ecomm_Short_Description: Sour taste with notes of diesel and citrus fruit.
Ecomm_Long_Description: LTRSR by Re-Up (Ultra Sour) is from East Coast Sour Diesel and MK Ultra lineage. It has mid-to-high-THC levels and a signature sour taste that is characterized by diesel and citrus fruit.

Ecomm_Short_Description: CBD-dominant, water-soluble drops
